name: 任务名字
desc: 任务描述
desc_tw: 任务描述
desc_en: 任务描述
desc_kr: 任务描述_韩
condition1: 额外条件1 (1-星级;2-阶数;3-资质)
condition1Arg: 额外条件1参数 ({星级/阶数/资质=数量})

name: Eliminate pests
desc: There's a pest infestation in the forest recently and there's a need for trainers to clear them with their Pokémons
desc_tw: 近期森林中的害蟲氾濫，需要各方精靈前去清除。
desc_en: There's a pest infestation in the forest recently and there's a need for trainers to clear them with their Pokémons
desc_kr: 최근에 숲에서 해충이 범람하여, 포켓몬을 보내 박멸이 필요함.

name: Pick berries
desc: It's the season of berries again! Organize an outing with the Pokémons to pick the berries!
desc_tw: 又到了樹果盛產的季節，和精靈組織一場採集樹果的郊遊吧！
desc_en: It's the season of berries again! Organize an outing with the Pokémons to pick the berries!
desc_kr: 과일 수확의 계절이 찾아왔습니다. 포켓몬들과 함께 과일을 따러 가세요!

name: Waste sorting
desc: Let's sort the waste in order to protect our environment.
desc_tw: 為了更好的保護環境，來進行垃圾分類吧。
desc_en: Let's sort the waste in order to protect our environment.
desc_kr: 환경을 지키기 위해, 쓰레기를 분리수거해주세요.

name: Missing Pokémon
desc: The trainer in town has lost his Pokémon. Help him find it.
desc_tw: 鎮上的訓練家把自己的精靈弄丟了，需要請求幫忙一起尋找。
desc_en: The trainer in town has lost his Pokémon. Help him find it.
desc_kr: 마을에서 어느 트레이너가 자신의 포켓몬을 잃어버렸답니다. 같이 찾아 주세요.

name: Spiritual Mentor
desc: Use Pokémons to comfort the lost villagers and relief the depressing mood.
desc_tw: 用精靈去溫暖失落的村民，釋放壓抑的心情。
desc_en: Use Pokémons to comfort the lost villagers and relief the depressing mood.
desc_kr: 낙심하는 마을 주민을 포켓몬으로 위로해 주고, 우울한 기분을 풀어주세요.

name: Help to find Pokémon
desc: Help rookie trainers train their Pokémons.
desc_tw: 幫助新手訓練家馴服自己的精靈。
desc_en: Help rookie trainers train their Pokémons.
desc_kr: 새로 온 트레이너의 포켓몬 훈련을 도와주세요.

name: Catch the criminal
desc: The police have found a Pokémon thief who has been wanted for years. Assist the police in their arrest!
desc_tw: 警方找到通緝多年偷盜精靈的小偷，協助員警進行抓捕！
desc_en: The police have found a Pokémon thief who has been wanted for years. Assist the police in their arrest!
desc_kr: 경찰이 수년간 수배한 포켓몬 도둑을 찾아냈습니다. 경찰을 도와 범인을 잡으세요!

name: Protect the villagers
desc: The wild Pokémons have often attacked the villagers in the town. Go and protect the villagers!
desc_tw: 野生的精靈最近暴亂，經常襲擊鎮上村民，請前去保護村民安全！
desc_en: The wild Pokémons have often attacked the villagers in the town. Go and protect the villagers!
desc_kr: 야생의 포켓몬들이 최근 폭동을 일으켜, 마을 주민을 습격하고 있습니다. 주민들을 지켜주세요!

name: Follow the target
desc: The police asked the trainer to assist in tracking the targets and reporting their whereabouts.
desc_tw: 員警請求訓練家説明跟蹤目標人物，並回饋行蹤。
desc_en: The police asked the trainer to assist in tracking the targets and reporting their whereabouts.
desc_kr: 경찰이 트레이너에게 타깃 인물을 추적하고 행적을 알려달라 요청했습니다.

name: Escort the Professor
desc: The professor has requested the Trainers Association to protect him and ensure his safe arrival at the destination.
desc_tw: 博士委託訓練家協會來護送自己，要求安全抵達目的地。
desc_en: The professor has requested the Trainers Association to protect him and ensure his safe arrival at the destination.
desc_kr: 박사님이 트레이너 협회에 자신을 목적지까지 안전하게 호송해달라 요청했습니다.

name: Escort the Document
desc: The mysterious organization requested for a trainer to protect and deliver the confidential documents.
desc_tw: 神秘機構委託訓練家來幫忙押運機密檔，完成後可獲得豐厚報酬。
desc_en: The mysterious organization requested for a trainer to protect and deliver the confidential documents.
desc_kr: 수수께끼의 기관이 트레이너에게 기밀문서 운송을 위탁했습니다. 완료하면 푸짐한 보수를 얻을 수 있습니다

name: Private Investigator
desc: The villagers privately requested help from the trainers to investigate the whereabouts of their missing partners.
desc_tw: 村民私下委託訓練家們來調查自己物件的行蹤。
desc_en: The villagers privately requested help from the trainers to investigate the whereabouts of their missing partners.
desc_kr: 마을 주민이 사적으로 트레이너들에게 대상의 행적을 조사해달라 위탁했습니다.

name: Alola Investigation
desc: Dispatch Pokémons to Alola region and find out whether there are wild Mews in the area.
desc_tw: 派遣精靈前往阿羅拉地區，調查當地是否有野生的夢幻出沒。
desc_en: Dispatch Pokémons to Alola region and find out whether there are wild Mews in the area.
desc_kr: 포켓몬을 알로라 지역으로 파견해, 야생의 뮤가 출몰했는지 조사하라 했습니다.

name: Soothe the Pokémon
desc: Soothe the Pokémons that hinders the citizens from traveling around in this city.
desc_tw: 把在本市擾亂市民正常出行的精靈安撫平定下來。
desc_en: Soothe the Pokémons that hinders the citizens from traveling around in this city.
desc_kr: 도시에서 시민들의 정상적인 외출을 방해하는 포켓몬을 달래주세요.

name: Kiwifruit
desc: Form a team of Pokémons to explore the forest and find kiwifruits.
desc_tw: 組織一隊精靈前往森林進行探索，需找一種名為奇異果實的食物。
desc_en: Form a team of Pokémons to explore the forest and find kiwifruits.
desc_kr: 포켓몬 팀을 꾸려 숲을 탐색하고, 키위라는 과일을 찾으세요.

name: Spiritual Mentor
desc: Use Pokémons to comfort the lost villagers and relief the depressing mood.
desc_tw: 用精靈去溫暖失落的村民，釋放壓抑的心情。

desc: Help rookie trainers train their Pokémons.

desc_kr: 새로 온 트레이너의 포켓몬 훈련을 도와주세요.

name: Catch the criminal
desc: The police have found a Pokémon thief who has been wanted for years. Assist the police in their arrest!
desc_tw: 警方找到通緝多年偷盜精靈的小偷，協助員警進行抓捕！
desc_en: The police have found a Pokémon thief who has been wanted for years. Assist the police in their arrest!
desc_kr: 경찰이 수년간 수배한 포켓몬 도둑을 찾아냈습니다. 경찰을 도와 범인을 잡으세요!

name: Protect the villagers
desc: The wild Pokémons have often attacked the villagers in the town. Go and protect the villagers!
desc_tw: 野生的精靈最近暴亂，經常襲擊鎮上村民，請前去保護村民安全！
desc_en: The wild Pokémons have often attacked the villagers in the town. Go and protect the villagers!
desc_kr: 야생의 포켓몬들이 최근 폭동을 일으켜, 마을 주민을 습격하고 있습니다. 주민들을 지켜주세요!

name: Follow the target
desc: The police asked the trainer to assist in tracking the targets and reporting their whereabouts.
desc_tw: 員警請求訓練家説明跟蹤目標人物，並回饋行蹤。
desc_en: The police asked the trainer to assist in tracking the targets and reporting their whereabouts.
desc_kr: 경찰이 트레이너에게 타깃 인물을 추적하고 행적을 알려달라 요청했습니다.

name: Escort the Professor
desc: The professor has requested the Trainers Association to protect him and ensure his safe arrival at the destination.
desc_tw: 博士委託訓練家協會來護送自己，要求安全抵達目的地。
desc_en: The professor has requested the Trainers Association to protect him and ensure his safe arrival at the destination.
desc_kr: 박사님이 트레이너 협회에 자신을 목적지까지 안전하게 호송해달라 요청했습니다.

name: Escort the Document
desc: The mysterious organization requested for a trainer to protect and deliver the confidential documents.
desc_tw: 神秘機構委託訓練家來幫忙押運機密檔，完成後可獲得豐厚報酬。
desc_en: The mysterious organization requested for a trainer to protect and deliver the confidential documents.
desc_kr: 수수께끼의 기관이 트레이너에게 기밀문서 운송을 위탁했습니다. 완료하면 푸짐한 보수를 얻을 수 있습니다

name: Private Investigator
desc: The villagers privately requested help from the trainers to investigate the whereabouts of their missing partners.
desc_tw: 村民私下委託訓練家們來調查自己物件的行蹤。
desc_en: The villagers privately requested help from the trainers to investigate the whereabouts of their missing partners.
desc_kr: 마을 주민이 사적으로 트레이너들에게 대상의 행적을 조사해달라 위탁했습니다.

name: Alola Investigation
desc: Dispatch Pokémons to Alola region and find out whether there are wild Mews in the area.
desc_tw: 派遣精靈前往阿羅拉地區，調查當地是否有野生的夢幻出沒。
desc_en: Dispatch Pokémons to Alola region and find out whether there are wild Mews in the area.
desc_kr: 포켓몬을 알로라 지역으로 파견해, 야생의 뮤가 출몰했는지 조사하라 했습니다.

name: Soothe the Pokémon
desc: Soothe the Pokémons that hinders the citizens from traveling around in this city.
desc_tw: 把在本市擾亂市民正常出行的精靈安撫平定下來。
desc_en: Soothe the Pokémons that hinders the citizens from traveling around in this city.
desc_kr: 도시에서 시민들의 정상적인 외출을 방해하는 포켓몬을 달래주세요.

name: Kiwifruit
desc: Form a team of Pokémons to explore the forest and find kiwifruits.
desc_tw: 組織一隊精靈前往森林進行探索，需找一種名為奇異果實的食物。
desc_en: Form a team of Pokémons to explore the forest and find kiwifruits.
desc_kr: 포켓몬 팀을 꾸려 숲을 탐색하고, 키위라는 과일을 찾으세요.

name: Eliminate pests
desc: There's a pest infestation in the forest recently and there's a need for trainers to clear them with their Pokémons
desc_tw: 近期森林中的害蟲氾濫，需要各方精靈前去清除。
desc_en: There's a pest infestation in the forest recently and there's a need for trainers to clear them with their Pokémons
desc_kr: 최근에 숲에서 해충이 범람하여, 포켓몬을 보내 박멸이 필요함.

name: Pick berries
desc: It's the season of berries again! Organize an outing with the Pokémons to pick the berries!
desc_tw: 又到了樹果盛產的季節，和精靈組織一場採集樹果的郊遊吧！
desc_en: It's the season of berries again! Organize an outing with the Pokémons to pick the berries!
desc_kr: 과일 수확의 계절이 찾아왔습니다. 포켓몬들과 함께 과일을 따러 가세요!

desc_kr: 경찰이 수년간 수배한 포켓몬 도둑을 찾아냈습니다. 경찰을 도와 범인을 잡으세요!

name: Protect the villagers
desc: The wild Pokémons have often attacked the villagers in the town. Go and protect the villagers!
desc_tw: 野生的精靈最近暴亂，經常襲擊鎮上村民，請前去保護村民安全！
desc_en: The wild Pokémons have often attacked the villagers in the town. Go and protect the villagers!
desc_kr: 야생의 포켓몬들이 최근 폭동을 일으켜, 마을 주민을 습격하고 있습니다. 주민들을 지켜주세요!

name: Follow the target
desc: The police asked the trainer to assist in tracking the targets and reporting their whereabouts.
desc_tw: 員警請求訓練家説明跟蹤目標人物，並回饋行蹤。
desc_en: The police asked the trainer to assist in tracking the targets and reporting their whereabouts.
desc_kr: 경찰이 트레이너에게 타깃 인물을 추적하고 행적을 알려달라 요청했습니다.

name: Escort the Professor
desc: The professor has requested the Trainers Association to protect him and ensure his safe arrival at the destination.
desc_tw: 博士委託訓練家協會來護送自己，要求安全抵達目的地。
desc_en: The professor has requested the Trainers Association to protect him and ensure his safe arrival at the destination.
desc_kr: 박사님이 트레이너 협회에 자신을 목적지까지 안전하게 호송해달라 요청했습니다.

name: Escort the Document
desc: The mysterious organization requested for a trainer to protect and deliver the confidential documents.
desc_tw: 神秘機構委託訓練家來幫忙押運機密檔，完成後可獲得豐厚報酬。
desc_en: The mysterious organization requested for a trainer to protect and deliver the confidential documents.
desc_kr: 수수께끼의 기관이 트레이너에게 기밀문서 운송을 위탁했습니다. 완료하면 푸짐한 보수를 얻을 수 있습니다

name: Private Investigator
desc: The villagers privately requested help from the trainers to investigate the whereabouts of their missing partners.
desc_tw: 村民私下委託訓練家們來調查自己物件的行蹤。
desc_en: The villagers privately requested help from the trainers to investigate the whereabouts of their missing partners.
desc_kr: 마을 주민이 사적으로 트레이너들에게 대상의 행적을 조사해달라 위탁했습니다.

name: Alola Investigation
desc: Dispatch Pokémons to Alola region and find out whether there are wild Mews in the area.
desc_tw: 派遣精靈前往阿羅拉地區，調查當地是否有野生的夢幻出沒。
desc_en: Dispatch Pokémons to Alola region and find out whether there are wild Mews in the area.
desc_kr: 포켓몬을 알로라 지역으로 파견해, 야생의 뮤가 출몰했는지 조사하라 했습니다.

name: Soothe the Pokémon
desc: Soothe the Pokémons that hinders the citizens from traveling around in this city.
desc_tw: 把在本市擾亂市民正常出行的精靈安撫平定下來。
desc_en: Soothe the Pokémons that hinders the citizens from traveling around in this city.
desc_kr: 도시에서 시민들의 정상적인 외출을 방해하는 포켓몬을 달래주세요.

name: Kiwifruit
desc: Form a team of Pokémons to explore the forest and find kiwifruits.
desc_tw: 組織一隊精靈前往森林進行探索，需找一種名為奇異果實的食物。
desc_en: Form a team of Pokémons to explore the forest and find kiwifruits.
desc_kr: 포켓몬 팀을 꾸려 숲을 탐색하고, 키위라는 과일을 찾으세요.

name: Eliminate pests
desc: There's a pest infestation in the forest recently and there's a need for trainers to clear them with their Pokémons
desc_tw: 近期森林中的害蟲氾濫，需要各方精靈前去清除。
desc_en: There's a pest infestation in the forest recently and there's a need for trainers to clear them with their Pokémons
desc_kr: 최근에 숲에서 해충이 범람하여, 포켓몬을 보내 박멸이 필요함.

name: Pick berries
desc: It's the season of berries again! Organize an outing with the Pokémons to pick the berries!
desc_tw: 又到了樹果盛產的季節，和精靈組織一場採集樹果的郊遊吧！
desc_en: It's the season of berries again! Organize an outing with the Pokémons to pick the berries!
desc_kr: 과일 수확의 계절이 찾아왔습니다. 포켓몬들과 함께 과일을 따러 가세요!

name: Waste sorting
desc: Let's sort the waste in order to protect our environment.
desc_tw: 為了更好的保護環境，來進行垃圾分類吧。
desc_en: Let's sort the waste in order to protect our environment.
desc_kr: 환경을 지키기 위해, 쓰레기를 분리수거해주세요.

name: Missing Pokémon
desc: The trainer in town has lost his Pokémon. Help him find it.
desc_tw: 鎮上的訓練家把自己的精靈弄丟了，需要請求幫忙一起尋找。
desc_en: The trainer in town has lost his Pokémon. Help him find it.
desc_kr: 마을에서 어느 트레이너가 자신의 포켓몬을 잃어버렸답니다. 같이 찾아 주세요.

name: Spiritual Mentor
desc: Use Pokémons to comfort the lost villagers and relief the depressing mood.
desc_tw: 用精靈去溫暖失落的村民，釋放壓抑的心情。
desc_en: Use Pokémons to comfort the lost villagers and relief the depressing mood.
desc_kr: 낙심하는 마을 주민을 포켓몬으로 위로해 주고, 우울한 기분을 풀어주세요.

name: Help to find Pokémon
desc: Help rookie trainers train their Pokémons.
desc_tw: 幫助新手訓練家馴服自己的精靈。
desc_en: Help rookie trainers train their Pokémons.
desc_kr: 새로 온 트레이너의 포켓몬 훈련을 도와주세요.

desc_en: The professor has requested the Trainers Association to protect him and ensure his safe arrival at the destination.
desc_kr: 박사님이 트레이너 협회에 자신을 목적지까지 안전하게 호송해달라 요청했습니다.

name: Escort the Document
desc: The mysterious organization requested for a trainer to protect and deliver the confidential documents.
desc_tw: 神秘機構委託訓練家來幫忙押運機密檔，完成後可獲得豐厚報酬。
desc_en: The mysterious organization requested for a trainer to protect and deliver the confidential documents.
desc_kr: 수수께끼의 기관이 트레이너에게 기밀문서 운송을 위탁했습니다. 완료하면 푸짐한 보수를 얻을 수 있습니다

name: Private Investigator
desc: The villagers privately requested help from the trainers to investigate the whereabouts of their missing partners.
desc_tw: 村民私下委託訓練家們來調查自己物件的行蹤。
desc_en: The villagers privately requested help from the trainers to investigate the whereabouts of their missing partners.
desc_kr: 마을 주민이 사적으로 트레이너들에게 대상의 행적을 조사해달라 위탁했습니다.

name: Alola Investigation
desc: Dispatch Pokémons to Alola region and find out whether there are wild Mews in the area.
desc_tw: 派遣精靈前往阿羅拉地區，調查當地是否有野生的夢幻出沒。
desc_en: Dispatch Pokémons to Alola region and find out whether there are wild Mews in the area.
desc_kr: 포켓몬을 알로라 지역으로 파견해, 야생의 뮤가 출몰했는지 조사하라 했습니다.

name: Soothe the Pokémon
desc: Soothe the Pokémons that hinders the citizens from traveling around in this city.
desc_tw: 把在本市擾亂市民正常出行的精靈安撫平定下來。
desc_en: Soothe the Pokémons that hinders the citizens from traveling around in this city.
desc_kr: 도시에서 시민들의 정상적인 외출을 방해하는 포켓몬을 달래주세요.

name: Kiwifruit
desc: Form a team of Pokémons to explore the forest and find kiwifruits.
desc_tw: 組織一隊精靈前往森林進行探索，需找一種名為奇異果實的食物。
desc_en: Form a team of Pokémons to explore the forest and find kiwifruits.
desc_kr: 포켓몬 팀을 꾸려 숲을 탐색하고, 키위라는 과일을 찾으세요.

name: Eliminate pests
desc: There's a pest infestation in the forest recently and there's a need for trainers to clear them with their Pokémons
desc_tw: 近期森林中的害蟲氾濫，需要各方精靈前去清除。
desc_en: There's a pest infestation in the forest recently and there's a need for trainers to clear them with their Pokémons
desc_kr: 최근에 숲에서 해충이 범람하여, 포켓몬을 보내 박멸이 필요함.

name: Pick berries
desc: It's the season of berries again! Organize an outing with the Pokémons to pick the berries!
desc_tw: 又到了樹果盛產的季節，和精靈組織一場採集樹果的郊遊吧！
desc_en: It's the season of berries again! Organize an outing with the Pokémons to pick the berries!
desc_kr: 과일 수확의 계절이 찾아왔습니다. 포켓몬들과 함께 과일을 따러 가세요!

name: Waste sorting
desc: Let's sort the waste in order to protect our environment.
desc_tw: 為了更好的保護環境，來進行垃圾分類吧。
desc_en: Let's sort the waste in order to protect our environment.
desc_kr: 환경을 지키기 위해, 쓰레기를 분리수거해주세요.

name: Missing Pokémon
desc: The trainer in town has lost his Pokémon. Help him find it.
desc_tw: 鎮上的訓練家把自己的精靈弄丟了，需要請求幫忙一起尋找。
desc_en: The trainer in town has lost his Pokémon. Help him find it.
desc_kr: 마을에서 어느 트레이너가 자신의 포켓몬을 잃어버렸답니다. 같이 찾아 주세요.

name: Spiritual Mentor
desc: Use Pokémons to comfort the lost villagers and relief the depressing mood.
desc_tw: 用精靈去溫暖失落的村民，釋放壓抑的心情。
desc_en: Use Pokémons to comfort the lost villagers and relief the depressing mood.
desc_kr: 낙심하는 마을 주민을 포켓몬으로 위로해 주고, 우울한 기분을 풀어주세요.

name: Help to find Pokémon
desc: Help rookie trainers train their Pokémons.
desc_tw: 幫助新手訓練家馴服自己的精靈。
desc_en: Help rookie trainers train their Pokémons.
desc_kr: 새로 온 트레이너의 포켓몬 훈련을 도와주세요.

name: Catch the criminal
desc: The police have found a Pokémon thief who has been wanted for years. Assist the police in their arrest!
desc_tw: 警方找到通緝多年偷盜精靈的小偷，協助員警進行抓捕！
desc_en: The police have found a Pokémon thief who has been wanted for years. Assist the police in their arrest!
desc_kr: 경찰이 수년간 수배한 포켓몬 도둑을 찾아냈습니다. 경찰을 도와 범인을 잡으세요!

name: Protect the villagers
desc: The wild Pokémons have often attacked the villagers in the town. Go and protect the villagers!
desc_tw: 野生的精靈最近暴亂，經常襲擊鎮上村民，請前去保護村民安全！
desc_en: The wild Pokémons have often attacked the villagers in the town. Go and protect the villagers!
desc_kr: 야생의 포켓몬들이 최근 폭동을 일으켜, 마을 주민을 습격하고 있습니다. 주민들을 지켜주세요!

name: Follow the target
desc: The police asked the trainer to assist in tracking the targets and reporting their whereabouts.
desc_tw: 員警請求訓練家説明跟蹤目標人物，並回饋行蹤。
desc_en: The police asked the trainer to assist in tracking the targets and reporting their whereabouts.
desc_kr: 경찰이 트레이너에게 타깃 인물을 추적하고 행적을 알려달라 요청했습니다.

desc_tw: 派遣精靈前往阿羅拉地區，調查當地是否有野生的夢幻出沒。
desc_en: Dispatch Pokémons to Alola region and find out whether there are wild Mews in the area.
desc_kr: 포켓몬을 알로라 지역으로 파견해, 야생의 뮤가 출몰했는지 조사하라 했습니다.

name: Soothe the Pokémon
desc: Soothe the Pokémons that hinders the citizens from traveling around in this city.
desc_tw: 把在本市擾亂市民正常出行的精靈安撫平定下來。
desc_en: Soothe the Pokémons that hinders the citizens from traveling around in this city.
desc_kr: 도시에서 시민들의 정상적인 외출을 방해하는 포켓몬을 달래주세요.

name: Kiwifruit
desc: Form a team of Pokémons to explore the forest and find kiwifruits.
desc_tw: 組織一隊精靈前往森林進行探索，需找一種名為奇異果實的食物。
desc_en: Form a team of Pokémons to explore the forest and find kiwifruits.
desc_kr: 포켓몬 팀을 꾸려 숲을 탐색하고, 키위라는 과일을 찾으세요.

name: Eliminate pests
desc: There's a pest infestation in the forest recently and there's a need for trainers to clear them with their Pokémons
desc_tw: 近期森林中的害蟲氾濫，需要各方精靈前去清除。
desc_en: There's a pest infestation in the forest recently and there's a need for trainers to clear them with their Pokémons
desc_kr: 최근에 숲에서 해충이 범람하여, 포켓몬을 보내 박멸이 필요함.

name: Pick berries
desc: It's the season of berries again! Organize an outing with the Pokémons to pick the berries!
desc_tw: 又到了樹果盛產的季節，和精靈組織一場採集樹果的郊遊吧！
desc_en: It's the season of berries again! Organize an outing with the Pokémons to pick the berries!
desc_kr: 과일 수확의 계절이 찾아왔습니다. 포켓몬들과 함께 과일을 따러 가세요!

name: Waste sorting
desc: Let's sort the waste in order to protect our environment.
desc_tw: 為了更好的保護環境，來進行垃圾分類吧。
desc_en: Let's sort the waste in order to protect our environment.
desc_kr: 환경을 지키기 위해, 쓰레기를 분리수거해주세요.

name: Missing Pokémon
desc: The trainer in town has lost his Pokémon. Help him find it.
desc_tw: 鎮上的訓練家把自己的精靈弄丟了，需要請求幫忙一起尋找。
desc_en: The trainer in town has lost his Pokémon. Help him find it.
desc_kr: 마을에서 어느 트레이너가 자신의 포켓몬을 잃어버렸답니다. 같이 찾아 주세요.

name: Spiritual Mentor
desc: Use Pokémons to comfort the lost villagers and relief the depressing mood.
desc_tw: 用精靈去溫暖失落的村民，釋放壓抑的心情。
desc_en: Use Pokémons to comfort the lost villagers and relief the depressing mood.
desc_kr: 낙심하는 마을 주민을 포켓몬으로 위로해 주고, 우울한 기분을 풀어주세요.

name: Help to find Pokémon
desc: Help rookie trainers train their Pokémons.
desc_tw: 幫助新手訓練家馴服自己的精靈。
desc_en: Help rookie trainers train their Pokémons.
desc_kr: 새로 온 트레이너의 포켓몬 훈련을 도와주세요.

name: Catch the criminal
desc: The police have found a Pokémon thief who has been wanted for years. Assist the police in their arrest!
desc_tw: 警方找到通緝多年偷盜精靈的小偷，協助員警進行抓捕！
desc_en: The police have found a Pokémon thief who has been wanted for years. Assist the police in their arrest!
desc_kr: 경찰이 수년간 수배한 포켓몬 도둑을 찾아냈습니다. 경찰을 도와 범인을 잡으세요!

name: Protect the villagers
desc: The wild Pokémons have often attacked the villagers in the town. Go and protect the villagers!
desc_tw: 野生的精靈最近暴亂，經常襲擊鎮上村民，請前去保護村民安全！
desc_en: The wild Pokémons have often attacked the villagers in the town. Go and protect the villagers!
desc_kr: 야생의 포켓몬들이 최근 폭동을 일으켜, 마을 주민을 습격하고 있습니다. 주민들을 지켜주세요!

name: Follow the target
desc: The police asked the trainer to assist in tracking the targets and reporting their whereabouts.
desc_tw: 員警請求訓練家説明跟蹤目標人物，並回饋行蹤。
desc_en: The police asked the trainer to assist in tracking the targets and reporting their whereabouts.
desc_kr: 경찰이 트레이너에게 타깃 인물을 추적하고 행적을 알려달라 요청했습니다.

name: Escort the Professor
desc: The professor has requested the Trainers Association to protect him and ensure his safe arrival at the destination.
desc_tw: 博士委託訓練家協會來護送自己，要求安全抵達目的地。
desc_en: The professor has requested the Trainers Association to protect him and ensure his safe arrival at the destination.
desc_kr: 박사님이 트레이너 협회에 자신을 목적지까지 안전하게 호송해달라 요청했습니다.

name: Escort the Document
desc: The mysterious organization requested for a trainer to protect and deliver the confidential documents.
desc_tw: 神秘機構委託訓練家來幫忙押運機密檔，完成後可獲得豐厚報酬。
desc_en: The mysterious organization requested for a trainer to protect and deliver the confidential documents.
desc_kr: 수수께끼의 기관이 트레이너에게 기밀문서 운송을 위탁했습니다. 완료하면 푸짐한 보수를 얻을 수 있습니다

name: Private Investigator
desc: The villagers privately requested help from the trainers to investigate the whereabouts of their missing partners.
desc_tw: 村民私下委託訓練家們來調查自己物件的行蹤。
desc_en: The villagers privately requested help from the trainers to investigate the whereabouts of their missing partners.
desc_kr: 마을 주민이 사적으로 트레이너들에게 대상의 행적을 조사해달라 위탁했습니다.

desc_tw: 派遣精靈前往阿羅拉地區，調查當地是否有野生的夢幻出沒。
desc_en: Dispatch Pokémons to Alola region and find out whether there are wild Mews in the area.

desc_en: There's a pest infestation in the forest recently and there's a need for trainers to clear them with their Pokémons
desc_kr: 최근에 숲에서 해충이 범람하여, 포켓몬을 보내 박멸이 필요함.

name: Pick berries
desc: It's the season of berries again! Organize an outing with the Pokémons to pick the berries!
desc_tw: 又到了樹果盛產的季節，和精靈組織一場採集樹果的郊遊吧！
desc_en: It's the season of berries again! Organize an outing with the Pokémons to pick the berries!
desc_kr: 과일 수확의 계절이 찾아왔습니다. 포켓몬들과 함께 과일을 따러 가세요!

name: Waste sorting
desc: Let's sort the waste in order to protect our environment.
desc_tw: 為了更好的保護環境，來進行垃圾分類吧。
desc_en: Let's sort the waste in order to protect our environment.
desc_kr: 환경을 지키기 위해, 쓰레기를 분리수거해주세요.

name: Missing Pokémon
desc: The trainer in town has lost his Pokémon. Help him find it.
desc_tw: 鎮上的訓練家把自己的精靈弄丟了，需要請求幫忙一起尋找。
desc_en: The trainer in town has lost his Pokémon. Help him find it.
desc_kr: 마을에서 어느 트레이너가 자신의 포켓몬을 잃어버렸답니다. 같이 찾아 주세요.

name: Spiritual Mentor
desc: Use Pokémons to comfort the lost villagers and relief the depressing mood.
desc_tw: 用精靈去溫暖失落的村民，釋放壓抑的心情。
desc_en: Use Pokémons to comfort the lost villagers and relief the depressing mood.
desc_kr: 낙심하는 마을 주민을 포켓몬으로 위로해 주고, 우울한 기분을 풀어주세요.

name: Help to find Pokémon
desc: Help rookie trainers train their Pokémons.
desc_tw: 幫助新手訓練家馴服自己的精靈。
desc_en: Help rookie trainers train their Pokémons.
desc_kr: 새로 온 트레이너의 포켓몬 훈련을 도와주세요.

name: Catch the criminal
desc: The police have found a Pokémon thief who has been wanted for years. Assist the police in their arrest!
desc_tw: 警方找到通緝多年偷盜精靈的小偷，協助員警進行抓捕！
desc_en: The police have found a Pokémon thief who has been wanted for years. Assist the police in their arrest!
desc_kr: 경찰이 수년간 수배한 포켓몬 도둑을 찾아냈습니다. 경찰을 도와 범인을 잡으세요!

name: Protect the villagers
desc: The wild Pokémons have often attacked the villagers in the town. Go and protect the villagers!
desc_tw: 野生的精靈最近暴亂，經常襲擊鎮上村民，請前去保護村民安全！
desc_en: The wild Pokémons have often attacked the villagers in the town. Go and protect the villagers!
desc_kr: 야생의 포켓몬들이 최근 폭동을 일으켜, 마을 주민을 습격하고 있습니다. 주민들을 지켜주세요!

name: Follow the target
desc: The police asked the trainer to assist in tracking the targets and reporting their whereabouts.
desc_tw: 員警請求訓練家説明跟蹤目標人物，並回饋行蹤。
desc_en: The police asked the trainer to assist in tracking the targets and reporting their whereabouts.
desc_kr: 경찰이 트레이너에게 타깃 인물을 추적하고 행적을 알려달라 요청했습니다.

name: Escort the Professor
desc: The professor has requested the Trainers Association to protect him and ensure his safe arrival at the destination.
desc_tw: 博士委託訓練家協會來護送自己，要求安全抵達目的地。
desc_en: The professor has requested the Trainers Association to protect him and ensure his safe arrival at the destination.
desc_kr: 박사님이 트레이너 협회에 자신을 목적지까지 안전하게 호송해달라 요청했습니다.

name: Escort the Document
desc: The mysterious organization requested for a trainer to protect and deliver the confidential documents.
desc_tw: 神秘機構委託訓練家來幫忙押運機密檔，完成後可獲得豐厚報酬。
desc_en: The mysterious organization requested for a trainer to protect and deliver the confidential documents.
desc_kr: 수수께끼의 기관이 트레이너에게 기밀문서 운송을 위탁했습니다. 완료하면 푸짐한 보수를 얻을 수 있습니다

name: Private Investigator
desc: The villagers privately requested help from the trainers to investigate the whereabouts of their missing partners.
desc_tw: 村民私下委託訓練家們來調查自己物件的行蹤。
desc_en: The villagers privately requested help from the trainers to investigate the whereabouts of their missing partners.
desc_kr: 마을 주민이 사적으로 트레이너들에게 대상의 행적을 조사해달라 위탁했습니다.

name: Alola Investigation
desc: Dispatch Pokémons to Alola region and find out whether there are wild Mews in the area.
desc_tw: 派遣精靈前往阿羅拉地區，調查當地是否有野生的夢幻出沒。
desc_en: Dispatch Pokémons to Alola region and find out whether there are wild Mews in the area.
desc_kr: 포켓몬을 알로라 지역으로 파견해, 야생의 뮤가 출몰했는지 조사하라 했습니다.

name: Soothe the Pokémon
desc: Soothe the Pokémons that hinders the citizens from traveling around in this city.
desc_tw: 把在本市擾亂市民正常出行的精靈安撫平定下來。
desc_en: Soothe the Pokémons that hinders the citizens from traveling around in this city.
desc_kr: 도시에서 시민들의 정상적인 외출을 방해하는 포켓몬을 달래주세요.

name: Kiwifruit
desc: Form a team of Pokémons to explore the forest and find kiwifruits.
desc_tw: 組織一隊精靈前往森林進行探索，需找一種名為奇異果實的食物。
desc_en: Form a team of Pokémons to explore the forest and find kiwifruits.
desc_kr: 포켓몬 팀을 꾸려 숲을 탐색하고, 키위라는 과일을 찾으세요.

desc_kr: 마을에서 어느 트레이너가 자신의 포켓몬을 잃어버렸답니다. 같이 찾아 주세요.

name: Spiritual Mentor
desc: Use Pokémons to comfort the lost villagers and relief the depressing mood.
desc_tw: 用精靈去溫暖失落的村民，釋放壓抑的心情。
desc_en: Use Pokémons to comfort the lost villagers and relief the depressing mood.
desc_kr: 낙심하는 마을 주민을 포켓몬으로 위로해 주고, 우울한 기분을 풀어주세요.

name: Help to find Pokémon
desc: Help rookie trainers train their Pokémons.
desc_tw: 幫助新手訓練家馴服自己的精靈。
desc_en: Help rookie trainers train their Pokémons.
desc_kr: 새로 온 트레이너의 포켓몬 훈련을 도와주세요.

name: Catch the criminal
desc: The police have found a Pokémon thief who has been wanted for years. Assist the police in their arrest!
desc_tw: 警方找到通緝多年偷盜精靈的小偷，協助員警進行抓捕！
desc_en: The police have found a Pokémon thief who has been wanted for years. Assist the police in their arrest!
desc_kr: 경찰이 수년간 수배한 포켓몬 도둑을 찾아냈습니다. 경찰을 도와 범인을 잡으세요!

name: Protect the villagers
desc: The wild Pokémons have often attacked the villagers in the town. Go and protect the villagers!
desc_tw: 野生的精靈最近暴亂，經常襲擊鎮上村民，請前去保護村民安全！
desc_en: The wild Pokémons have often attacked the villagers in the town. Go and protect the villagers!
desc_kr: 야생의 포켓몬들이 최근 폭동을 일으켜, 마을 주민을 습격하고 있습니다. 주민들을 지켜주세요!

name: Follow the target
desc: The police asked the trainer to assist in tracking the targets and reporting their whereabouts.
desc_tw: 員警請求訓練家説明跟蹤目標人物，並回饋行蹤。
desc_en: The police asked the trainer to assist in tracking the targets and reporting their whereabouts.
desc_kr: 경찰이 트레이너에게 타깃 인물을 추적하고 행적을 알려달라 요청했습니다.

name: Escort the Professor
desc: The professor has requested the Trainers Association to protect him and ensure his safe arrival at the destination.
desc_tw: 博士委託訓練家協會來護送自己，要求安全抵達目的地。
desc_en: The professor has requested the Trainers Association to protect him and ensure his safe arrival at the destination.
desc_kr: 박사님이 트레이너 협회에 자신을 목적지까지 안전하게 호송해달라 요청했습니다.

name: Escort the Document
desc: The mysterious organization requested for a trainer to protect and deliver the confidential documents.
desc_tw: 神秘機構委託訓練家來幫忙押運機密檔，完成後可獲得豐厚報酬。
desc_en: The mysterious organization requested for a trainer to protect and deliver the confidential documents.
desc_kr: 수수께끼의 기관이 트레이너에게 기밀문서 운송을 위탁했습니다. 완료하면 푸짐한 보수를 얻을 수 있습니다

name: Private Investigator
desc: The villagers privately requested help from the trainers to investigate the whereabouts of their missing partners.
desc_tw: 村民私下委託訓練家們來調查自己物件的行蹤。
desc_en: The villagers privately requested help from the trainers to investigate the whereabouts of their missing partners.
desc_kr: 마을 주민이 사적으로 트레이너들에게 대상의 행적을 조사해달라 위탁했습니다.

name: Alola Investigation
desc: Dispatch Pokémons to Alola region and find out whether there are wild Mews in the area.
desc_tw: 派遣精靈前往阿羅拉地區，調查當地是否有野生的夢幻出沒。
desc_en: Dispatch Pokémons to Alola region and find out whether there are wild Mews in the area.
desc_kr: 포켓몬을 알로라 지역으로 파견해, 야생의 뮤가 출몰했는지 조사하라 했습니다.

name: Soothe the Pokémon
desc: Soothe the Pokémons that hinders the citizens from traveling around in this city.
desc_tw: 把在本市擾亂市民正常出行的精靈安撫平定下來。
desc_en: Soothe the Pokémons that hinders the citizens from traveling around in this city.
desc_kr: 도시에서 시민들의 정상적인 외출을 방해하는 포켓몬을 달래주세요.

name: Kiwifruit
desc: Form a team of Pokémons to explore the forest and find kiwifruits.
desc_tw: 組織一隊精靈前往森林進行探索，需找一種名為奇異果實的食物。
desc_en: Form a team of Pokémons to explore the forest and find kiwifruits.
desc_kr: 포켓몬 팀을 꾸려 숲을 탐색하고, 키위라는 과일을 찾으세요.

name: Eliminate pests
desc: There's a pest infestation in the forest recently and there's a need for trainers to clear them with their Pokémons
desc_tw: 近期森林中的害蟲氾濫，需要各方精靈前去清除。
desc_en: There's a pest infestation in the forest recently and there's a need for trainers to clear them with their Pokémons
desc_kr: 최근에 숲에서 해충이 범람하여, 포켓몬을 보내 박멸이 필요함.

name: Pick berries
desc: It's the season of berries again! Organize an outing with the Pokémons to pick the berries!
desc_tw: 又到了樹果盛產的季節，和精靈組織一場採集樹果的郊遊吧！
desc_en: It's the season of berries again! Organize an outing with the Pokémons to pick the berries!
desc_kr: 과일 수확의 계절이 찾아왔습니다. 포켓몬들과 함께 과일을 따러 가세요!

name: Waste sorting
desc: Let's sort the waste in order to protect our environment.
desc_tw: 為了更好的保護環境，來進行垃圾分類吧。
desc_en: Let's sort the waste in order to protect our environment.
desc_kr: 환경을 지키기 위해, 쓰레기를 분리수거해주세요.

desc: The wild Pokémons have often attacked the villagers in the town. Go and protect the villagers!
desc_tw: 野生的精靈最近暴亂，經常襲擊鎮上村民，請前去保護村民安全！
desc_en: The wild Pokémons have often attacked the villagers in the town. Go and protect the villagers!
desc_kr: 야생의 포켓몬들이 최근 폭동을 일으켜, 마을 주민을 습격하고 있습니다. 주민들을 지켜주세요!

name: Follow the target
desc: The police asked the trainer to assist in tracking the targets and reporting their whereabouts.
desc_tw: 員警請求訓練家説明跟蹤目標人物，並回饋行蹤。
desc_en: The police asked the trainer to assist in tracking the targets and reporting their whereabouts.
desc_kr: 경찰이 트레이너에게 타깃 인물을 추적하고 행적을 알려달라 요청했습니다.

name: Escort the Professor
desc: The professor has requested the Trainers Association to protect him and ensure his safe arrival at the destination.
desc_tw: 博士委託訓練家協會來護送自己，要求安全抵達目的地。
desc_en: The professor has requested the Trainers Association to protect him and ensure his safe arrival at the destination.
desc_kr: 박사님이 트레이너 협회에 자신을 목적지까지 안전하게 호송해달라 요청했습니다.

name: Escort the Document
desc: The mysterious organization requested for a trainer to protect and deliver the confidential documents.
desc_tw: 神秘機構委託訓練家來幫忙押運機密檔，完成後可獲得豐厚報酬。
desc_en: The mysterious organization requested for a trainer to protect and deliver the confidential documents.
desc_kr: 수수께끼의 기관이 트레이너에게 기밀문서 운송을 위탁했습니다. 완료하면 푸짐한 보수를 얻을 수 있습니다

name: Private Investigator
desc: The villagers privately requested help from the trainers to investigate the whereabouts of their missing partners.
desc_tw: 村民私下委託訓練家們來調查自己物件的行蹤。
desc_en: The villagers privately requested help from the trainers to investigate the whereabouts of their missing partners.
desc_kr: 마을 주민이 사적으로 트레이너들에게 대상의 행적을 조사해달라 위탁했습니다.

name: Alola Investigation
desc: Dispatch Pokémons to Alola region and find out whether there are wild Mews in the area.
desc_tw: 派遣精靈前往阿羅拉地區，調查當地是否有野生的夢幻出沒。
desc_en: Dispatch Pokémons to Alola region and find out whether there are wild Mews in the area.
desc_kr: 포켓몬을 알로라 지역으로 파견해, 야생의 뮤가 출몰했는지 조사하라 했습니다.

name: Soothe the Pokémon
desc: Soothe the Pokémons that hinders the citizens from traveling around in this city.
desc_tw: 把在本市擾亂市民正常出行的精靈安撫平定下來。
desc_en: Soothe the Pokémons that hinders the citizens from traveling around in this city.
desc_kr: 도시에서 시민들의 정상적인 외출을 방해하는 포켓몬을 달래주세요.

name: Kiwifruit
desc: Form a team of Pokémons to explore the forest and find kiwifruits.
desc_tw: 組織一隊精靈前往森林進行探索，需找一種名為奇異果實的食物。
desc_en: Form a team of Pokémons to explore the forest and find kiwifruits.
desc_kr: 포켓몬 팀을 꾸려 숲을 탐색하고, 키위라는 과일을 찾으세요.

name: Eliminate pests
desc: There's a pest infestation in the forest recently and there's a need for trainers to clear them with their Pokémons
desc_tw: 近期森林中的害蟲氾濫，需要各方精靈前去清除。
desc_en: There's a pest infestation in the forest recently and there's a need for trainers to clear them with their Pokémons
desc_kr: 최근에 숲에서 해충이 범람하여, 포켓몬을 보내 박멸이 필요함.

name: Pick berries
desc: It's the season of berries again! Organize an outing with the Pokémons to pick the berries!
desc_tw: 又到了樹果盛產的季節，和精靈組織一場採集樹果的郊遊吧！
desc_en: It's the season of berries again! Organize an outing with the Pokémons to pick the berries!
desc_kr: 과일 수확의 계절이 찾아왔습니다. 포켓몬들과 함께 과일을 따러 가세요!

name: Waste sorting
desc: Let's sort the waste in order to protect our environment.
desc_tw: 為了更好的保護環境，來進行垃圾分類吧。
desc_en: Let's sort the waste in order to protect our environment.
desc_kr: 환경을 지키기 위해, 쓰레기를 분리수거해주세요.

name: Missing Pokémon
desc: The trainer in town has lost his Pokémon. Help him find it.
desc_tw: 鎮上的訓練家把自己的精靈弄丟了，需要請求幫忙一起尋找。
desc_en: The trainer in town has lost his Pokémon. Help him find it.
desc_kr: 마을에서 어느 트레이너가 자신의 포켓몬을 잃어버렸답니다. 같이 찾아 주세요.

name: Spiritual Mentor
desc: Use Pokémons to comfort the lost villagers and relief the depressing mood.
desc_tw: 用精靈去溫暖失落的村民，釋放壓抑的心情。
desc_en: Use Pokémons to comfort the lost villagers and relief the depressing mood.
desc_kr: 낙심하는 마을 주민을 포켓몬으로 위로해 주고, 우울한 기분을 풀어주세요.

name: Help to find Pokémon
desc: Help rookie trainers train their Pokémons.
desc_tw: 幫助新手訓練家馴服自己的精靈。
desc_en: Help rookie trainers train their Pokémons.
desc_kr: 새로 온 트레이너의 포켓몬 훈련을 도와주세요.

name: Catch the criminal
desc: The police have found a Pokémon thief who has been wanted for years. Assist the police in their arrest!
desc_tw: 警方找到通緝多年偷盜精靈的小偷，協助員警進行抓捕！
desc_en: The police have found a Pokémon thief who has been wanted for years. Assist the police in their arrest!
desc_kr: 경찰이 수년간 수배한 포켓몬 도둑을 찾아냈습니다. 경찰을 도와 범인을 잡으세요!

desc_kr: 박사님이 트레이너 협회에 자신을 목적지까지 안전하게 호송해달라 요청했습니다.

name: Escort the Document
desc: The mysterious organization requested for a trainer to protect and deliver the confidential documents.
desc_tw: 神秘機構委託訓練家來幫忙押運機密檔，完成後可獲得豐厚報酬。
desc_en: The mysterious organization requested for a trainer to protect and deliver the confidential documents.
desc_kr: 수수께끼의 기관이 트레이너에게 기밀문서 운송을 위탁했습니다. 완료하면 푸짐한 보수를 얻을 수 있습니다

name: Private Investigator
desc: The villagers privately requested help from the trainers to investigate the whereabouts of their missing partners.
desc_tw: 村民私下委託訓練家們來調查自己物件的行蹤。
desc_en: The villagers privately requested help from the trainers to investigate the whereabouts of their missing partners.
desc_kr: 마을 주민이 사적으로 트레이너들에게 대상의 행적을 조사해달라 위탁했습니다.

name: Alola Investigation
desc: Dispatch Pokémons to Alola region and find out whether there are wild Mews in the area.
desc_tw: 派遣精靈前往阿羅拉地區，調查當地是否有野生的夢幻出沒。
desc_en: Dispatch Pokémons to Alola region and find out whether there are wild Mews in the area.
desc_kr: 포켓몬을 알로라 지역으로 파견해, 야생의 뮤가 출몰했는지 조사하라 했습니다.

name: Soothe the Pokémon
desc: Soothe the Pokémons that hinders the citizens from traveling around in this city.
desc_tw: 把在本市擾亂市民正常出行的精靈安撫平定下來。
desc_en: Soothe the Pokémons that hinders the citizens from traveling around in this city.
desc_kr: 도시에서 시민들의 정상적인 외출을 방해하는 포켓몬을 달래주세요.

name: Kiwifruit
desc: Form a team of Pokémons to explore the forest and find kiwifruits.
desc_tw: 組織一隊精靈前往森林進行探索，需找一種名為奇異果實的食物。
desc_en: Form a team of Pokémons to explore the forest and find kiwifruits.
desc_kr: 포켓몬 팀을 꾸려 숲을 탐색하고, 키위라는 과일을 찾으세요.

name: Eliminate pests
desc: There's a pest infestation in the forest recently and there's a need for trainers to clear them with their Pokémons
desc_tw: 近期森林中的害蟲氾濫，需要各方精靈前去清除。
desc_en: There's a pest infestation in the forest recently and there's a need for trainers to clear them with their Pokémons
desc_kr: 최근에 숲에서 해충이 범람하여, 포켓몬을 보내 박멸이 필요함.

name: Pick berries
desc: It's the season of berries again! Organize an outing with the Pokémons to pick the berries!
desc_tw: 又到了樹果盛產的季節，和精靈組織一場採集樹果的郊遊吧！
desc_en: It's the season of berries again! Organize an outing with the Pokémons to pick the berries!
desc_kr: 과일 수확의 계절이 찾아왔습니다. 포켓몬들과 함께 과일을 따러 가세요!

name: Waste sorting
desc: Let's sort the waste in order to protect our environment.
desc_tw: 為了更好的保護環境，來進行垃圾分類吧。
desc_en: Let's sort the waste in order to protect our environment.
desc_kr: 환경을 지키기 위해, 쓰레기를 분리수거해주세요.

name: Missing Pokémon
desc: The trainer in town has lost his Pokémon. Help him find it.
desc_tw: 鎮上的訓練家把自己的精靈弄丟了，需要請求幫忙一起尋找。
desc_en: The trainer in town has lost his Pokémon. Help him find it.
desc_kr: 마을에서 어느 트레이너가 자신의 포켓몬을 잃어버렸답니다. 같이 찾아 주세요.

name: Spiritual Mentor
desc: Use Pokémons to comfort the lost villagers and relief the depressing mood.
desc_tw: 用精靈去溫暖失落的村民，釋放壓抑的心情。
desc_en: Use Pokémons to comfort the lost villagers and relief the depressing mood.
desc_kr: 낙심하는 마을 주민을 포켓몬으로 위로해 주고, 우울한 기분을 풀어주세요.

name: Help to find Pokémon
desc: Help rookie trainers train their Pokémons.
desc_tw: 幫助新手訓練家馴服自己的精靈。
desc_en: Help rookie trainers train their Pokémons.
desc_kr: 새로 온 트레이너의 포켓몬 훈련을 도와주세요.

name: Catch the criminal
desc: The police have found a Pokémon thief who has been wanted for years. Assist the police in their arrest!
desc_tw: 警方找到通緝多年偷盜精靈的小偷，協助員警進行抓捕！
desc_en: The police have found a Pokémon thief who has been wanted for years. Assist the police in their arrest!
desc_kr: 경찰이 수년간 수배한 포켓몬 도둑을 찾아냈습니다. 경찰을 도와 범인을 잡으세요!

name: Protect the villagers
desc: The wild Pokémons have often attacked the villagers in the town. Go and protect the villagers!
desc_tw: 野生的精靈最近暴亂，經常襲擊鎮上村民，請前去保護村民安全！
desc_en: The wild Pokémons have often attacked the villagers in the town. Go and protect the villagers!
desc_kr: 야생의 포켓몬들이 최근 폭동을 일으켜, 마을 주민을 습격하고 있습니다. 주민들을 지켜주세요!

name: Follow the target

desc_tw: 員警請求訓練家説明跟蹤目標人物，並回饋行蹤。
desc_en: The police asked the trainer to assist in tracking the targets and reporting their whereabouts.
desc_kr: 경찰이 트레이너에게 타깃 인물을 추적하고 행적을 알려달라 요청했습니다.

desc_en: Dispatch Pokémons to Alola region and find out whether there are wild Mews in the area.
desc_kr: 포켓몬을 알로라 지역으로 파견해, 야생의 뮤가 출몰했는지 조사하라 했습니다.

name: Soothe the Pokémon
desc: Soothe the Pokémons that hinders the citizens from traveling around in this city.
desc_tw: 把在本市擾亂市民正常出行的精靈安撫平定下來。
desc_en: Soothe the Pokémons that hinders the citizens from traveling around in this city.
desc_kr: 도시에서 시민들의 정상적인 외출을 방해하는 포켓몬을 달래주세요.

name: Kiwifruit
desc: Form a team of Pokémons to explore the forest and find kiwifruits.
desc_tw: 組織一隊精靈前往森林進行探索，需找一種名為奇異果實的食物。
desc_en: Form a team of Pokémons to explore the forest and find kiwifruits.
desc_kr: 포켓몬 팀을 꾸려 숲을 탐색하고, 키위라는 과일을 찾으세요.

name: Eliminate pests
desc: There's a pest infestation in the forest recently and there's a need for trainers to clear them with their Pokémons
desc_tw: 近期森林中的害蟲氾濫，需要各方精靈前去清除。
desc_en: There's a pest infestation in the forest recently and there's a need for trainers to clear them with their Pokémons
desc_kr: 최근에 숲에서 해충이 범람하여, 포켓몬을 보내 박멸이 필요함.

name: Pick berries
desc: It's the season of berries again! Organize an outing with the Pokémons to pick the berries!
desc_tw: 又到了樹果盛產的季節，和精靈組織一場採集樹果的郊遊吧！
desc_en: It's the season of berries again! Organize an outing with the Pokémons to pick the berries!
desc_kr: 과일 수확의 계절이 찾아왔습니다. 포켓몬들과 함께 과일을 따러 가세요!

name: Waste sorting
desc: Let's sort the waste in order to protect our environment.
desc_tw: 為了更好的保護環境，來進行垃圾分類吧。
desc_en: Let's sort the waste in order to protect our environment.
desc_kr: 환경을 지키기 위해, 쓰레기를 분리수거해주세요.

name: Missing Pokémon
desc: The trainer in town has lost his Pokémon. Help him find it.
desc_tw: 鎮上的訓練家把自己的精靈弄丟了，需要請求幫忙一起尋找。
desc_en: The trainer in town has lost his Pokémon. Help him find it.
desc_kr: 마을에서 어느 트레이너가 자신의 포켓몬을 잃어버렸답니다. 같이 찾아 주세요.

name: Spiritual Mentor
desc: Use Pokémons to comfort the lost villagers and relief the depressing mood.
desc_tw: 用精靈去溫暖失落的村民，釋放壓抑的心情。
desc_en: Use Pokémons to comfort the lost villagers and relief the depressing mood.
desc_kr: 낙심하는 마을 주민을 포켓몬으로 위로해 주고, 우울한 기분을 풀어주세요.

name: Help to find Pokémon
desc: Help rookie trainers train their Pokémons.
desc_tw: 幫助新手訓練家馴服自己的精靈。
desc_en: Help rookie trainers train their Pokémons.
desc_kr: 새로 온 트레이너의 포켓몬 훈련을 도와주세요.

name: Catch the criminal
desc: The police have found a Pokémon thief who has been wanted for years. Assist the police in their arrest!
desc_tw: 警方找到通緝多年偷盜精靈的小偷，協助員警進行抓捕！
desc_en: The police have found a Pokémon thief who has been wanted for years. Assist the police in their arrest!
desc_kr: 경찰이 수년간 수배한 포켓몬 도둑을 찾아냈습니다. 경찰을 도와 범인을 잡으세요!

name: Protect the villagers
desc: The wild Pokémons have often attacked the villagers in the town. Go and protect the villagers!
desc_tw: 野生的精靈最近暴亂，經常襲擊鎮上村民，請前去保護村民安全！
desc_en: The wild Pokémons have often attacked the villagers in the town. Go and protect the villagers!
desc_kr: 야생의 포켓몬들이 최근 폭동을 일으켜, 마을 주민을 습격하고 있습니다. 주민들을 지켜주세요!

name: Follow the target
desc: The police asked the trainer to assist in tracking the targets and reporting their whereabouts.
desc_tw: 員警請求訓練家説明跟蹤目標人物，並回饋行蹤。
desc_en: The police asked the trainer to assist in tracking the targets and reporting their whereabouts.
desc_kr: 경찰이 트레이너에게 타깃 인물을 추적하고 행적을 알려달라 요청했습니다.

name: Escort the Professor
desc: The professor has requested the Trainers Association to protect him and ensure his safe arrival at the destination.
desc_tw: 博士委託訓練家協會來護送自己，要求安全抵達目的地。
desc_en: The professor has requested the Trainers Association to protect him and ensure his safe arrival at the destination.
desc_kr: 박사님이 트레이너 협회에 자신을 목적지까지 안전하게 호송해달라 요청했습니다.

name: Escort the Document
desc: The mysterious organization requested for a trainer to protect and deliver the confidential documents.
desc_tw: 神秘機構委託訓練家來幫忙押運機密檔，完成後可獲得豐厚報酬。
desc_en: The mysterious organization requested for a trainer to protect and deliver the confidential documents.
desc_kr: 수수께끼의 기관이 트레이너에게 기밀문서 운송을 위탁했습니다. 완료하면 푸짐한 보수를 얻을 수 있습니다

name: Private Investigator
desc: The villagers privately requested help from the trainers to investigate the whereabouts of their missing partners.
desc_tw: 村民私下委託訓練家們來調查自己物件的行蹤。
desc_en: The villagers privately requested help from the trainers to investigate the whereabouts of their missing partners.
desc_kr: 마을 주민이 사적으로 트레이너들에게 대상의 행적을 조사해달라 위탁했습니다.

desc_en: There's a pest infestation in the forest recently and there's a need for trainers to clear them with their Pokémons
desc_kr: 최근에 숲에서 해충이 범람하여, 포켓몬을 보내 박멸이 필요함.

name: Pick berries
desc: It's the season of berries again! Organize an outing with the Pokémons to pick the berries!
desc_tw: 又到了樹果盛產的季節，和精靈組織一場採集樹果的郊遊吧！
desc_en: It's the season of berries again! Organize an outing with the Pokémons to pick the berries!
desc_kr: 과일 수확의 계절이 찾아왔습니다. 포켓몬들과 함께 과일을 따러 가세요!

name: Waste sorting
desc: Let's sort the waste in order to protect our environment.
desc_tw: 為了更好的保護環境，來進行垃圾分類吧。
desc_en: Let's sort the waste in order to protect our environment.
desc_kr: 환경을 지키기 위해, 쓰레기를 분리수거해주세요.

name: Missing Pokémon
desc: The trainer in town has lost his Pokémon. Help him find it.
desc_tw: 鎮上的訓練家把自己的精靈弄丟了，需要請求幫忙一起尋找。
desc_en: The trainer in town has lost his Pokémon. Help him find it.
desc_kr: 마을에서 어느 트레이너가 자신의 포켓몬을 잃어버렸답니다. 같이 찾아 주세요.

name: Spiritual Mentor
desc: Use Pokémons to comfort the lost villagers and relief the depressing mood.
desc_tw: 用精靈去溫暖失落的村民，釋放壓抑的心情。
desc_en: Use Pokémons to comfort the lost villagers and relief the depressing mood.
desc_kr: 낙심하는 마을 주민을 포켓몬으로 위로해 주고, 우울한 기분을 풀어주세요.

name: Help to find Pokémon
desc: Help rookie trainers train their Pokémons.
desc_tw: 幫助新手訓練家馴服自己的精靈。
desc_en: Help rookie trainers train their Pokémons.
desc_kr: 새로 온 트레이너의 포켓몬 훈련을 도와주세요.

name: Catch the criminal
desc: The police have found a Pokémon thief who has been wanted for years. Assist the police in their arrest!
desc_tw: 警方找到通緝多年偷盜精靈的小偷，協助員警進行抓捕！
desc_en: The police have found a Pokémon thief who has been wanted for years. Assist the police in their arrest!
desc_kr: 경찰이 수년간 수배한 포켓몬 도둑을 찾아냈습니다. 경찰을 도와 범인을 잡으세요!

name: Protect the villagers
desc: The wild Pokémons have often attacked the villagers in the town. Go and protect the villagers!
desc_tw: 野生的精靈最近暴亂，經常襲擊鎮上村民，請前去保護村民安全！
desc_en: The wild Pokémons have often attacked the villagers in the town. Go and protect the villagers!
desc_kr: 야생의 포켓몬들이 최근 폭동을 일으켜, 마을 주민을 습격하고 있습니다. 주민들을 지켜주세요!

name: Follow the target
desc: The police asked the trainer to assist in tracking the targets and reporting their whereabouts.
desc_tw: 員警請求訓練家説明跟蹤目標人物，並回饋行蹤。
desc_en: The police asked the trainer to assist in tracking the targets and reporting their whereabouts.
desc_kr: 경찰이 트레이너에게 타깃 인물을 추적하고 행적을 알려달라 요청했습니다.

name: Escort the Professor
desc: The professor has requested the Trainers Association to protect him and ensure his safe arrival at the destination.
desc_tw: 博士委託訓練家協會來護送自己，要求安全抵達目的地。
desc_en: The professor has requested the Trainers Association to protect him and ensure his safe arrival at the destination.
desc_kr: 박사님이 트레이너 협회에 자신을 목적지까지 안전하게 호송해달라 요청했습니다.

name: Escort the Document
desc: The mysterious organization requested for a trainer to protect and deliver the confidential documents.
desc_tw: 神秘機構委託訓練家來幫忙押運機密檔，完成後可獲得豐厚報酬。
desc_en: The mysterious organization requested for a trainer to protect and deliver the confidential documents.
desc_kr: 수수께끼의 기관이 트레이너에게 기밀문서 운송을 위탁했습니다. 완료하면 푸짐한 보수를 얻을 수 있습니다

name: Private Investigator
desc: The villagers privately requested help from the trainers to investigate the whereabouts of their missing partners.
desc_tw: 村民私下委託訓練家們來調查自己物件的行蹤。
desc_en: The villagers privately requested help from the trainers to investigate the whereabouts of their missing partners.
desc_kr: 마을 주민이 사적으로 트레이너들에게 대상의 행적을 조사해달라 위탁했습니다.

name: Alola Investigation
desc: Dispatch Pokémons to Alola region and find out whether there are wild Mews in the area.
desc_tw: 派遣精靈前往阿羅拉地區，調查當地是否有野生的夢幻出沒。
desc_en: Dispatch Pokémons to Alola region and find out whether there are wild Mews in the area.
desc_kr: 포켓몬을 알로라 지역으로 파견해, 야생의 뮤가 출몰했는지 조사하라 했습니다.

name: Soothe the Pokémon
desc: Soothe the Pokémons that hinders the citizens from traveling around in this city.
desc_tw: 把在本市擾亂市民正常出行的精靈安撫平定下來。
desc_en: Soothe the Pokémons that hinders the citizens from traveling around in this city.
desc_kr: 도시에서 시민들의 정상적인 외출을 방해하는 포켓몬을 달래주세요.

name: Kiwifruit
desc: Form a team of Pokémons to explore the forest and find kiwifruits.
desc_tw: 組織一隊精靈前往森林進行探索，需找一種名為奇異果實的食物。
desc_en: Form a team of Pokémons to explore the forest and find kiwifruits.
desc_kr: 포켓몬 팀을 꾸려 숲을 탐색하고, 키위라는 과일을 찾으세요.

desc_kr: 마을에서 어느 트레이너가 자신의 포켓몬을 잃어버렸답니다. 같이 찾아 주세요.

name: Spiritual Mentor
desc: Use Pokémons to comfort the lost villagers and relief the depressing mood.
desc_tw: 用精靈去溫暖失落的村民，釋放壓抑的心情。
desc_en: Use Pokémons to comfort the lost villagers and relief the depressing mood.
desc_kr: 낙심하는 마을 주민을 포켓몬으로 위로해 주고, 우울한 기분을 풀어주세요.

name: Help to find Pokémon
desc: Help rookie trainers train their Pokémons.
desc_tw: 幫助新手訓練家馴服自己的精靈。
desc_en: Help rookie trainers train their Pokémons.
desc_kr: 새로 온 트레이너의 포켓몬 훈련을 도와주세요.

name: Catch the criminal
desc: The police have found a Pokémon thief who has been wanted for years. Assist the police in their arrest!
desc_tw: 警方找到通緝多年偷盜精靈的小偷，協助員警進行抓捕！
desc_en: The police have found a Pokémon thief who has been wanted for years. Assist the police in their arrest!
desc_kr: 경찰이 수년간 수배한 포켓몬 도둑을 찾아냈습니다. 경찰을 도와 범인을 잡으세요!

name: Protect the villagers
desc: The wild Pokémons have often attacked the villagers in the town. Go and protect the villagers!
desc_tw: 野生的精靈最近暴亂，經常襲擊鎮上村民，請前去保護村民安全！
desc_en: The wild Pokémons have often attacked the villagers in the town. Go and protect the villagers!
desc_kr: 야생의 포켓몬들이 최근 폭동을 일으켜, 마을 주민을 습격하고 있습니다. 주민들을 지켜주세요!

name: Follow the target
desc: The police asked the trainer to assist in tracking the targets and reporting their whereabouts.
desc_tw: 員警請求訓練家説明跟蹤目標人物，並回饋行蹤。
desc_en: The police asked the trainer to assist in tracking the targets and reporting their whereabouts.
desc_kr: 경찰이 트레이너에게 타깃 인물을 추적하고 행적을 알려달라 요청했습니다.

name: Escort the Professor
desc: The professor has requested the Trainers Association to protect him and ensure his safe arrival at the destination.
desc_tw: 博士委託訓練家協會來護送自己，要求安全抵達目的地。
desc_en: The professor has requested the Trainers Association to protect him and ensure his safe arrival at the destination.
desc_kr: 박사님이 트레이너 협회에 자신을 목적지까지 안전하게 호송해달라 요청했습니다.

name: Escort the Document
desc: The mysterious organization requested for a trainer to protect and deliver the confidential documents.
desc_tw: 神秘機構委託訓練家來幫忙押運機密檔，完成後可獲得豐厚報酬。
desc_en: The mysterious organization requested for a trainer to protect and deliver the confidential documents.
desc_kr: 수수께끼의 기관이 트레이너에게 기밀문서 운송을 위탁했습니다. 완료하면 푸짐한 보수를 얻을 수 있습니다

name: Private Investigator
desc: The villagers privately requested help from the trainers to investigate the whereabouts of their missing partners.
desc_tw: 村民私下委託訓練家們來調查自己物件的行蹤。
desc_en: The villagers privately requested help from the trainers to investigate the whereabouts of their missing partners.
desc_kr: 마을 주민이 사적으로 트레이너들에게 대상의 행적을 조사해달라 위탁했습니다.

name: Alola Investigation
desc: Dispatch Pokémons to Alola region and find out whether there are wild Mews in the area.
desc_tw: 派遣精靈前往阿羅拉地區，調查當地是否有野生的夢幻出沒。
desc_en: Dispatch Pokémons to Alola region and find out whether there are wild Mews in the area.
desc_kr: 포켓몬을 알로라 지역으로 파견해, 야생의 뮤가 출몰했는지 조사하라 했습니다.

name: Soothe the Pokémon
desc: Soothe the Pokémons that hinders the citizens from traveling around in this city.
desc_tw: 把在本市擾亂市民正常出行的精靈安撫平定下來。
desc_en: Soothe the Pokémons that hinders the citizens from traveling around in this city.
desc_kr: 도시에서 시민들의 정상적인 외출을 방해하는 포켓몬을 달래주세요.

name: Kiwifruit
desc: Form a team of Pokémons to explore the forest and find kiwifruits.
desc_tw: 組織一隊精靈前往森林進行探索，需找一種名為奇異果實的食物。
desc_en: Form a team of Pokémons to explore the forest and find kiwifruits.
desc_kr: 포켓몬 팀을 꾸려 숲을 탐색하고, 키위라는 과일을 찾으세요.

name: Eliminate pests
desc: There's a pest infestation in the forest recently and there's a need for trainers to clear them with their Pokémons
desc_tw: 近期森林中的害蟲氾濫，需要各方精靈前去清除。
desc_en: There's a pest infestation in the forest recently and there's a need for trainers to clear them with their Pokémons
desc_kr: 최근에 숲에서 해충이 범람하여, 포켓몬을 보내 박멸이 필요함.

name: Pick berries
desc: It's the season of berries again! Organize an outing with the Pokémons to pick the berries!
desc_tw: 又到了樹果盛產的季節，和精靈組織一場採集樹果的郊遊吧！
desc_en: It's the season of berries again! Organize an outing with the Pokémons to pick the berries!
desc_kr: 과일 수확의 계절이 찾아왔습니다. 포켓몬들과 함께 과일을 따러 가세요!

name: Waste sorting
desc: Let's sort the waste in order to protect our environment.
desc_tw: 為了更好的保護環境，來進行垃圾分類吧。
desc_en: Let's sort the waste in order to protect our environment.
desc_kr: 환경을 지키기 위해, 쓰레기를 분리수거해주세요.

desc: The wild Pokémons have often attacked the villagers in the town. Go and protect the villagers!
desc_tw: 野生的精靈最近暴亂，經常襲擊鎮上村民，請前去保護村民安全！
desc_en: The wild Pokémons have often attacked the villagers in the town. Go and protect the villagers!
desc_kr: 야생의 포켓몬들이 최근 폭동을 일으켜, 마을 주민을 습격하고 있습니다. 주민들을 지켜주세요!

name: Follow the target
desc: The police asked the trainer to assist in tracking the targets and reporting their whereabouts.
desc_tw: 員警請求訓練家説明跟蹤目標人物，並回饋行蹤。
desc_en: The police asked the trainer to assist in tracking the targets and reporting their whereabouts.
desc_kr: 경찰이 트레이너에게 타깃 인물을 추적하고 행적을 알려달라 요청했습니다.

name: Escort the Professor
desc: The professor has requested the Trainers Association to protect him and ensure his safe arrival at the destination.
desc_tw: 博士委託訓練家協會來護送自己，要求安全抵達目的地。
desc_en: The professor has requested the Trainers Association to protect him and ensure his safe arrival at the destination.
desc_kr: 박사님이 트레이너 협회에 자신을 목적지까지 안전하게 호송해달라 요청했습니다.

name: Escort the Document
desc: The mysterious organization requested for a trainer to protect and deliver the confidential documents.
desc_tw: 神秘機構委託訓練家來幫忙押運機密檔，完成後可獲得豐厚報酬。
desc_en: The mysterious organization requested for a trainer to protect and deliver the confidential documents.
desc_kr: 수수께끼의 기관이 트레이너에게 기밀문서 운송을 위탁했습니다. 완료하면 푸짐한 보수를 얻을 수 있습니다

name: Private Investigator
desc: The villagers privately requested help from the trainers to investigate the whereabouts of their missing partners.
desc_tw: 村民私下委託訓練家們來調查自己物件的行蹤。
desc_en: The villagers privately requested help from the trainers to investigate the whereabouts of their missing partners.
desc_kr: 마을 주민이 사적으로 트레이너들에게 대상의 행적을 조사해달라 위탁했습니다.

name: Alola Investigation
desc: Dispatch Pokémons to Alola region and find out whether there are wild Mews in the area.
desc_tw: 派遣精靈前往阿羅拉地區，調查當地是否有野生的夢幻出沒。
desc_en: Dispatch Pokémons to Alola region and find out whether there are wild Mews in the area.
desc_kr: 포켓몬을 알로라 지역으로 파견해, 야생의 뮤가 출몰했는지 조사하라 했습니다.

name: Soothe the Pokémon
desc: Soothe the Pokémons that hinders the citizens from traveling around in this city.
desc_tw: 把在本市擾亂市民正常出行的精靈安撫平定下來。
desc_en: Soothe the Pokémons that hinders the citizens from traveling around in this city.
desc_kr: 도시에서 시민들의 정상적인 외출을 방해하는 포켓몬을 달래주세요.

name: Kiwifruit
desc: Form a team of Pokémons to explore the forest and find kiwifruits.
desc_tw: 組織一隊精靈前往森林進行探索，需找一種名為奇異果實的食物。
desc_en: Form a team of Pokémons to explore the forest and find kiwifruits.
desc_kr: 포켓몬 팀을 꾸려 숲을 탐색하고, 키위라는 과일을 찾으세요.

name: Eliminate pests
desc: There's a pest infestation in the forest recently and there's a need for trainers to clear them with their Pokémons
desc_tw: 近期森林中的害蟲氾濫，需要各方精靈前去清除。
desc_en: There's a pest infestation in the forest recently and there's a need for trainers to clear them with their Pokémons
desc_kr: 최근에 숲에서 해충이 범람하여, 포켓몬을 보내 박멸이 필요함.

name: Pick berries
desc: It's the season of berries again! Organize an outing with the Pokémons to pick the berries!
desc_tw: 又到了樹果盛產的季節，和精靈組織一場採集樹果的郊遊吧！
desc_en: It's the season of berries again! Organize an outing with the Pokémons to pick the berries!
desc_kr: 과일 수확의 계절이 찾아왔습니다. 포켓몬들과 함께 과일을 따러 가세요!

name: Waste sorting
desc: Let's sort the waste in order to protect our environment.
desc_tw: 為了更好的保護環境，來進行垃圾分類吧。
desc_en: Let's sort the waste in order to protect our environment.
desc_kr: 환경을 지키기 위해, 쓰레기를 분리수거해주세요.

name: Missing Pokémon
desc: The trainer in town has lost his Pokémon. Help him find it.
desc_tw: 鎮上的訓練家把自己的精靈弄丟了，需要請求幫忙一起尋找。
desc_en: The trainer in town has lost his Pokémon. Help him find it.
desc_kr: 마을에서 어느 트레이너가 자신의 포켓몬을 잃어버렸답니다. 같이 찾아 주세요.

name: Spiritual Mentor
desc: Use Pokémons to comfort the lost villagers and relief the depressing mood.
desc_tw: 用精靈去溫暖失落的村民，釋放壓抑的心情。
desc_en: Use Pokémons to comfort the lost villagers and relief the depressing mood.
desc_kr: 낙심하는 마을 주민을 포켓몬으로 위로해 주고, 우울한 기분을 풀어주세요.

name: Help to find Pokémon
desc: Help rookie trainers train their Pokémons.
desc_tw: 幫助新手訓練家馴服自己的精靈。
desc_en: Help rookie trainers train their Pokémons.
desc_kr: 새로 온 트레이너의 포켓몬 훈련을 도와주세요.

name: Catch the criminal
desc: The police have found a Pokémon thief who has been wanted for years. Assist the police in their arrest!
desc_tw: 警方找到通緝多年偷盜精靈的小偷，協助員警進行抓捕！
desc_en: The police have found a Pokémon thief who has been wanted for years. Assist the police in their arrest!
desc_kr: 경찰이 수년간 수배한 포켓몬 도둑을 찾아냈습니다. 경찰을 도와 범인을 잡으세요!

desc_kr: 박사님이 트레이너 협회에 자신을 목적지까지 안전하게 호송해달라 요청했습니다.

name: Escort the Document
desc: The mysterious organization requested for a trainer to protect and deliver the confidential documents.
desc_tw: 神秘機構委託訓練家來幫忙押運機密檔，完成後可獲得豐厚報酬。
desc_en: The mysterious organization requested for a trainer to protect and deliver the confidential documents.
desc_kr: 수수께끼의 기관이 트레이너에게 기밀문서 운송을 위탁했습니다. 완료하면 푸짐한 보수를 얻을 수 있습니다

name: Private Investigator
desc: The villagers privately requested help from the trainers to investigate the whereabouts of their missing partners.
desc_tw: 村民私下委託訓練家們來調查自己物件的行蹤。
desc_en: The villagers privately requested help from the trainers to investigate the whereabouts of their missing partners.
desc_kr: 마을 주민이 사적으로 트레이너들에게 대상의 행적을 조사해달라 위탁했습니다.

name: Alola Investigation
desc: Dispatch Pokémons to Alola region and find out whether there are wild Mews in the area.
desc_tw: 派遣精靈前往阿羅拉地區，調查當地是否有野生的夢幻出沒。
desc_en: Dispatch Pokémons to Alola region and find out whether there are wild Mews in the area.
desc_kr: 포켓몬을 알로라 지역으로 파견해, 야생의 뮤가 출몰했는지 조사하라 했습니다.

name: Soothe the Pokémon
desc: Soothe the Pokémons that hinders the citizens from traveling around in this city.
desc_tw: 把在本市擾亂市民正常出行的精靈安撫平定下來。
desc_en: Soothe the Pokémons that hinders the citizens from traveling around in this city.
desc_kr: 도시에서 시민들의 정상적인 외출을 방해하는 포켓몬을 달래주세요.

name: Kiwifruit
desc: Form a team of Pokémons to explore the forest and find kiwifruits.
desc_tw: 組織一隊精靈前往森林進行探索，需找一種名為奇異果實的食物。
desc_en: Form a team of Pokémons to explore the forest and find kiwifruits.
desc_kr: 포켓몬 팀을 꾸려 숲을 탐색하고, 키위라는 과일을 찾으세요.

name: Eliminate pests
desc: There's a pest infestation in the forest recently and there's a need for trainers to clear them with their Pokémons
desc_tw: 近期森林中的害蟲氾濫，需要各方精靈前去清除。
desc_en: There's a pest infestation in the forest recently and there's a need for trainers to clear them with their Pokémons
desc_kr: 최근에 숲에서 해충이 범람하여, 포켓몬을 보내 박멸이 필요함.

name: Pick berries
desc: It's the season of berries again! Organize an outing with the Pokémons to pick the berries!
desc_tw: 又到了樹果盛產的季節，和精靈組織一場採集樹果的郊遊吧！
desc_en: It's the season of berries again! Organize an outing with the Pokémons to pick the berries!
desc_kr: 과일 수확의 계절이 찾아왔습니다. 포켓몬들과 함께 과일을 따러 가세요!

name: Waste sorting
desc: Let's sort the waste in order to protect our environment.
desc_tw: 為了更好的保護環境，來進行垃圾分類吧。
desc_en: Let's sort the waste in order to protect our environment.
desc_kr: 환경을 지키기 위해, 쓰레기를 분리수거해주세요.

name: Missing Pokémon
desc: The trainer in town has lost his Pokémon. Help him find it.
desc_tw: 鎮上的訓練家把自己的精靈弄丟了，需要請求幫忙一起尋找。
desc_en: The trainer in town has lost his Pokémon. Help him find it.
desc_kr: 마을에서 어느 트레이너가 자신의 포켓몬을 잃어버렸답니다. 같이 찾아 주세요.

name: Spiritual Mentor
desc: Use Pokémons to comfort the lost villagers and relief the depressing mood.
desc_tw: 用精靈去溫暖失落的村民，釋放壓抑的心情。
desc_en: Use Pokémons to comfort the lost villagers and relief the depressing mood.
desc_kr: 낙심하는 마을 주민을 포켓몬으로 위로해 주고, 우울한 기분을 풀어주세요.

name: Help to find Pokémon
desc: Help rookie trainers train their Pokémons.
desc_tw: 幫助新手訓練家馴服自己的精靈。
desc_en: Help rookie trainers train their Pokémons.
desc_kr: 새로 온 트레이너의 포켓몬 훈련을 도와주세요.

name: Catch the criminal
desc: The police have found a Pokémon thief who has been wanted for years. Assist the police in their arrest!
desc_tw: 警方找到通緝多年偷盜精靈的小偷，協助員警進行抓捕！
desc_en: The police have found a Pokémon thief who has been wanted for years. Assist the police in their arrest!
desc_kr: 경찰이 수년간 수배한 포켓몬 도둑을 찾아냈습니다. 경찰을 도와 범인을 잡으세요!

name: Protect the villagers
desc: The wild Pokémons have often attacked the villagers in the town. Go and protect the villagers!
desc_tw: 野生的精靈最近暴亂，經常襲擊鎮上村民，請前去保護村民安全！
desc_en: The wild Pokémons have often attacked the villagers in the town. Go and protect the villagers!
desc_kr: 야생의 포켓몬들이 최근 폭동을 일으켜, 마을 주민을 습격하고 있습니다. 주민들을 지켜주세요!

name: Follow the target

desc_tw: 員警請求訓練家説明跟蹤目標人物，並回饋行蹤。
desc_en: The police asked the trainer to assist in tracking the targets and reporting their whereabouts.
desc_kr: 경찰이 트레이너에게 타깃 인물을 추적하고 행적을 알려달라 요청했습니다.

desc_en: Dispatch Pokémons to Alola region and find out whether there are wild Mews in the area.
desc_kr: 포켓몬을 알로라 지역으로 파견해, 야생의 뮤가 출몰했는지 조사하라 했습니다.

name: Soothe the Pokémon
desc: Soothe the Pokémons that hinders the citizens from traveling around in this city.
desc_tw: 把在本市擾亂市民正常出行的精靈安撫平定下來。
desc_en: Soothe the Pokémons that hinders the citizens from traveling around in this city.
desc_kr: 도시에서 시민들의 정상적인 외출을 방해하는 포켓몬을 달래주세요.

name: Kiwifruit
desc: Form a team of Pokémons to explore the forest and find kiwifruits.
desc_tw: 組織一隊精靈前往森林進行探索，需找一種名為奇異果實的食物。
desc_en: Form a team of Pokémons to explore the forest and find kiwifruits.
desc_kr: 포켓몬 팀을 꾸려 숲을 탐색하고, 키위라는 과일을 찾으세요.

name: Eliminate pests
desc: There's a pest infestation in the forest recently and there's a need for trainers to clear them with their Pokémons
desc_tw: 近期森林中的害蟲氾濫，需要各方精靈前去清除。
desc_en: There's a pest infestation in the forest recently and there's a need for trainers to clear them with their Pokémons
desc_kr: 최근에 숲에서 해충이 범람하여, 포켓몬을 보내 박멸이 필요함.

name: Pick berries
desc: It's the season of berries again! Organize an outing with the Pokémons to pick the berries!
desc_tw: 又到了樹果盛產的季節，和精靈組織一場採集樹果的郊遊吧！
desc_en: It's the season of berries again! Organize an outing with the Pokémons to pick the berries!
desc_kr: 과일 수확의 계절이 찾아왔습니다. 포켓몬들과 함께 과일을 따러 가세요!

name: Waste sorting
desc: Let's sort the waste in order to protect our environment.
desc_tw: 為了更好的保護環境，來進行垃圾分類吧。
desc_en: Let's sort the waste in order to protect our environment.
desc_kr: 환경을 지키기 위해, 쓰레기를 분리수거해주세요.

name: Missing Pokémon
desc: The trainer in town has lost his Pokémon. Help him find it.
desc_tw: 鎮上的訓練家把自己的精靈弄丟了，需要請求幫忙一起尋找。
desc_en: The trainer in town has lost his Pokémon. Help him find it.
desc_kr: 마을에서 어느 트레이너가 자신의 포켓몬을 잃어버렸답니다. 같이 찾아 주세요.

name: Spiritual Mentor
desc: Use Pokémons to comfort the lost villagers and relief the depressing mood.
desc_tw: 用精靈去溫暖失落的村民，釋放壓抑的心情。
desc_en: Use Pokémons to comfort the lost villagers and relief the depressing mood.
desc_kr: 낙심하는 마을 주민을 포켓몬으로 위로해 주고, 우울한 기분을 풀어주세요.

name: Help to find Pokémon
desc: Help rookie trainers train their Pokémons.
desc_tw: 幫助新手訓練家馴服自己的精靈。
desc_en: Help rookie trainers train their Pokémons.
desc_kr: 새로 온 트레이너의 포켓몬 훈련을 도와주세요.

name: Catch the criminal
desc: The police have found a Pokémon thief who has been wanted for years. Assist the police in their arrest!
desc_tw: 警方找到通緝多年偷盜精靈的小偷，協助員警進行抓捕！
desc_en: The police have found a Pokémon thief who has been wanted for years. Assist the police in their arrest!
desc_kr: 경찰이 수년간 수배한 포켓몬 도둑을 찾아냈습니다. 경찰을 도와 범인을 잡으세요!

name: Protect the villagers
desc: The wild Pokémons have often attacked the villagers in the town. Go and protect the villagers!
desc_tw: 野生的精靈最近暴亂，經常襲擊鎮上村民，請前去保護村民安全！
desc_en: The wild Pokémons have often attacked the villagers in the town. Go and protect the villagers!
desc_kr: 야생의 포켓몬들이 최근 폭동을 일으켜, 마을 주민을 습격하고 있습니다. 주민들을 지켜주세요!

name: Follow the target
desc: The police asked the trainer to assist in tracking the targets and reporting their whereabouts.
desc_tw: 員警請求訓練家説明跟蹤目標人物，並回饋行蹤。
desc_en: The police asked the trainer to assist in tracking the targets and reporting their whereabouts.
desc_kr: 경찰이 트레이너에게 타깃 인물을 추적하고 행적을 알려달라 요청했습니다.

name: Escort the Professor
desc: The professor has requested the Trainers Association to protect him and ensure his safe arrival at the destination.
desc_tw: 博士委託訓練家協會來護送自己，要求安全抵達目的地。
desc_en: The professor has requested the Trainers Association to protect him and ensure his safe arrival at the destination.
desc_kr: 박사님이 트레이너 협회에 자신을 목적지까지 안전하게 호송해달라 요청했습니다.

name: Escort the Document
desc: The mysterious organization requested for a trainer to protect and deliver the confidential documents.
desc_tw: 神秘機構委託訓練家來幫忙押運機密檔，完成後可獲得豐厚報酬。
desc_en: The mysterious organization requested for a trainer to protect and deliver the confidential documents.
desc_kr: 수수께끼의 기관이 트레이너에게 기밀문서 운송을 위탁했습니다. 완료하면 푸짐한 보수를 얻을 수 있습니다

name: Private Investigator
desc: The villagers privately requested help from the trainers to investigate the whereabouts of their missing partners.
desc_tw: 村民私下委託訓練家們來調查自己物件的行蹤。
desc_en: The villagers privately requested help from the trainers to investigate the whereabouts of their missing partners.
desc_kr: 마을 주민이 사적으로 트레이너들에게 대상의 행적을 조사해달라 위탁했습니다.

desc_en: There's a pest infestation in the forest recently and there's a need for trainers to clear them with their Pokémons
desc_kr: 최근에 숲에서 해충이 범람하여, 포켓몬을 보내 박멸이 필요함.

name: Pick berries
desc: It's the season of berries again! Organize an outing with the Pokémons to pick the berries!
desc_tw: 又到了樹果盛產的季節，和精靈組織一場採集樹果的郊遊吧！
desc_en: It's the season of berries again! Organize an outing with the Pokémons to pick the berries!
desc_kr: 과일 수확의 계절이 찾아왔습니다. 포켓몬들과 함께 과일을 따러 가세요!

name: Waste sorting
desc: Let's sort the waste in order to protect our environment.
desc_tw: 為了更好的保護環境，來進行垃圾分類吧。
desc_en: Let's sort the waste in order to protect our environment.
desc_kr: 환경을 지키기 위해, 쓰레기를 분리수거해주세요.

name: Missing Pokémon
desc: The trainer in town has lost his Pokémon. Help him find it.
desc_tw: 鎮上的訓練家把自己的精靈弄丟了，需要請求幫忙一起尋找。
desc_en: The trainer in town has lost his Pokémon. Help him find it.
desc_kr: 마을에서 어느 트레이너가 자신의 포켓몬을 잃어버렸답니다. 같이 찾아 주세요.

name: Spiritual Mentor
desc: Use Pokémons to comfort the lost villagers and relief the depressing mood.
desc_tw: 用精靈去溫暖失落的村民，釋放壓抑的心情。
desc_en: Use Pokémons to comfort the lost villagers and relief the depressing mood.
desc_kr: 낙심하는 마을 주민을 포켓몬으로 위로해 주고, 우울한 기분을 풀어주세요.

name: Help to find Pokémon
desc: Help rookie trainers train their Pokémons.
desc_tw: 幫助新手訓練家馴服自己的精靈。
desc_en: Help rookie trainers train their Pokémons.
desc_kr: 새로 온 트레이너의 포켓몬 훈련을 도와주세요.

name: Catch the criminal
desc: The police have found a Pokémon thief who has been wanted for years. Assist the police in their arrest!
desc_tw: 警方找到通緝多年偷盜精靈的小偷，協助員警進行抓捕！
desc_en: The police have found a Pokémon thief who has been wanted for years. Assist the police in their arrest!
desc_kr: 경찰이 수년간 수배한 포켓몬 도둑을 찾아냈습니다. 경찰을 도와 범인을 잡으세요!

name: Protect the villagers
desc: The wild Pokémons have often attacked the villagers in the town. Go and protect the villagers!
desc_tw: 野生的精靈最近暴亂，經常襲擊鎮上村民，請前去保護村民安全！
desc_en: The wild Pokémons have often attacked the villagers in the town. Go and protect the villagers!
desc_kr: 야생의 포켓몬들이 최근 폭동을 일으켜, 마을 주민을 습격하고 있습니다. 주민들을 지켜주세요!

name: Follow the target
desc: The police asked the trainer to assist in tracking the targets and reporting their whereabouts.
desc_tw: 員警請求訓練家説明跟蹤目標人物，並回饋行蹤。
desc_en: The police asked the trainer to assist in tracking the targets and reporting their whereabouts.
desc_kr: 경찰이 트레이너에게 타깃 인물을 추적하고 행적을 알려달라 요청했습니다.

name: Escort the Professor
desc: The professor has requested the Trainers Association to protect him and ensure his safe arrival at the destination.
desc_tw: 博士委託訓練家協會來護送自己，要求安全抵達目的地。
desc_en: The professor has requested the Trainers Association to protect him and ensure his safe arrival at the destination.
desc_kr: 박사님이 트레이너 협회에 자신을 목적지까지 안전하게 호송해달라 요청했습니다.

name: Escort the Document
desc: The mysterious organization requested for a trainer to protect and deliver the confidential documents.
desc_tw: 神秘機構委託訓練家來幫忙押運機密檔，完成後可獲得豐厚報酬。
desc_en: The mysterious organization requested for a trainer to protect and deliver the confidential documents.
desc_kr: 수수께끼의 기관이 트레이너에게 기밀문서 운송을 위탁했습니다. 완료하면 푸짐한 보수를 얻을 수 있습니다

name: Private Investigator
desc: The villagers privately requested help from the trainers to investigate the whereabouts of their missing partners.
desc_tw: 村民私下委託訓練家們來調查自己物件的行蹤。
desc_en: The villagers privately requested help from the trainers to investigate the whereabouts of their missing partners.
desc_kr: 마을 주민이 사적으로 트레이너들에게 대상의 행적을 조사해달라 위탁했습니다.

name: Alola Investigation
desc: Dispatch Pokémons to Alola region and find out whether there are wild Mews in the area.
desc_tw: 派遣精靈前往阿羅拉地區，調查當地是否有野生的夢幻出沒。
desc_en: Dispatch Pokémons to Alola region and find out whether there are wild Mews in the area.
desc_kr: 포켓몬을 알로라 지역으로 파견해, 야생의 뮤가 출몰했는지 조사하라 했습니다.

name: Soothe the Pokémon
desc: Soothe the Pokémons that hinders the citizens from traveling around in this city.
desc_tw: 把在本市擾亂市民正常出行的精靈安撫平定下來。
desc_en: Soothe the Pokémons that hinders the citizens from traveling around in this city.
desc_kr: 도시에서 시민들의 정상적인 외출을 방해하는 포켓몬을 달래주세요.

name: Kiwifruit
desc: Form a team of Pokémons to explore the forest and find kiwifruits.
desc_tw: 組織一隊精靈前往森林進行探索，需找一種名為奇異果實的食物。
desc_en: Form a team of Pokémons to explore the forest and find kiwifruits.
desc_kr: 포켓몬 팀을 꾸려 숲을 탐색하고, 키위라는 과일을 찾으세요.

desc_kr: 마을에서 어느 트레이너가 자신의 포켓몬을 잃어버렸답니다. 같이 찾아 주세요.

name: Spiritual Mentor
desc: Use Pokémons to comfort the lost villagers and relief the depressing mood.
desc_tw: 用精靈去溫暖失落的村民，釋放壓抑的心情。
desc_en: Use Pokémons to comfort the lost villagers and relief the depressing mood.
desc_kr: 낙심하는 마을 주민을 포켓몬으로 위로해 주고, 우울한 기분을 풀어주세요.

name: Help to find Pokémon
desc: Help rookie trainers train their Pokémons.
desc_tw: 幫助新手訓練家馴服自己的精靈。
desc_en: Help rookie trainers train their Pokémons.
desc_kr: 새로 온 트레이너의 포켓몬 훈련을 도와주세요.

name: Catch the criminal
desc: The police have found a Pokémon thief who has been wanted for years. Assist the police in their arrest!
desc_tw: 警方找到通緝多年偷盜精靈的小偷，協助員警進行抓捕！
desc_en: The police have found a Pokémon thief who has been wanted for years. Assist the police in their arrest!
desc_kr: 경찰이 수년간 수배한 포켓몬 도둑을 찾아냈습니다. 경찰을 도와 범인을 잡으세요!

name: Protect the villagers
desc: The wild Pokémons have often attacked the villagers in the town. Go and protect the villagers!
desc_tw: 野生的精靈最近暴亂，經常襲擊鎮上村民，請前去保護村民安全！
desc_en: The wild Pokémons have often attacked the villagers in the town. Go and protect the villagers!
desc_kr: 야생의 포켓몬들이 최근 폭동을 일으켜, 마을 주민을 습격하고 있습니다. 주민들을 지켜주세요!

name: Follow the target
desc: The police asked the trainer to assist in tracking the targets and reporting their whereabouts.
desc_tw: 員警請求訓練家説明跟蹤目標人物，並回饋行蹤。
desc_en: The police asked the trainer to assist in tracking the targets and reporting their whereabouts.
desc_kr: 경찰이 트레이너에게 타깃 인물을 추적하고 행적을 알려달라 요청했습니다.

name: Escort the Professor
desc: The professor has requested the Trainers Association to protect him and ensure his safe arrival at the destination.
desc_tw: 博士委託訓練家協會來護送自己，要求安全抵達目的地。
desc_en: The professor has requested the Trainers Association to protect him and ensure his safe arrival at the destination.
desc_kr: 박사님이 트레이너 협회에 자신을 목적지까지 안전하게 호송해달라 요청했습니다.

name: Escort the Document
desc: The mysterious organization requested for a trainer to protect and deliver the confidential documents.
desc_tw: 神秘機構委託訓練家來幫忙押運機密檔，完成後可獲得豐厚報酬。
desc_en: The mysterious organization requested for a trainer to protect and deliver the confidential documents.
desc_kr: 수수께끼의 기관이 트레이너에게 기밀문서 운송을 위탁했습니다. 완료하면 푸짐한 보수를 얻을 수 있습니다

name: Private Investigator
desc: The villagers privately requested help from the trainers to investigate the whereabouts of their missing partners.
desc_tw: 村民私下委託訓練家們來調查自己物件的行蹤。
desc_en: The villagers privately requested help from the trainers to investigate the whereabouts of their missing partners.
desc_kr: 마을 주민이 사적으로 트레이너들에게 대상의 행적을 조사해달라 위탁했습니다.

name: Alola Investigation
desc: Dispatch Pokémons to Alola region and find out whether there are wild Mews in the area.
desc_tw: 派遣精靈前往阿羅拉地區，調查當地是否有野生的夢幻出沒。
desc_en: Dispatch Pokémons to Alola region and find out whether there are wild Mews in the area.
desc_kr: 포켓몬을 알로라 지역으로 파견해, 야생의 뮤가 출몰했는지 조사하라 했습니다.

name: Soothe the Pokémon
desc: Soothe the Pokémons that hinders the citizens from traveling around in this city.
desc_tw: 把在本市擾亂市民正常出行的精靈安撫平定下來。
desc_en: Soothe the Pokémons that hinders the citizens from traveling around in this city.
desc_kr: 도시에서 시민들의 정상적인 외출을 방해하는 포켓몬을 달래주세요.

name: Kiwifruit
desc: Form a team of Pokémons to explore the forest and find kiwifruits.
desc_tw: 組織一隊精靈前往森林進行探索，需找一種名為奇異果實的食物。
desc_en: Form a team of Pokémons to explore the forest and find kiwifruits.
desc_kr: 포켓몬 팀을 꾸려 숲을 탐색하고, 키위라는 과일을 찾으세요.

name: Eliminate pests
desc: There's a pest infestation in the forest recently and there's a need for trainers to clear them with their Pokémons
desc_tw: 近期森林中的害蟲氾濫，需要各方精靈前去清除。
desc_en: There's a pest infestation in the forest recently and there's a need for trainers to clear them with their Pokémons
desc_kr: 최근에 숲에서 해충이 범람하여, 포켓몬을 보내 박멸이 필요함.

name: Pick berries
desc: It's the season of berries again! Organize an outing with the Pokémons to pick the berries!
desc_tw: 又到了樹果盛產的季節，和精靈組織一場採集樹果的郊遊吧！
desc_en: It's the season of berries again! Organize an outing with the Pokémons to pick the berries!
desc_kr: 과일 수확의 계절이 찾아왔습니다. 포켓몬들과 함께 과일을 따러 가세요!

name: Waste sorting
desc: Let's sort the waste in order to protect our environment.
desc_tw: 為了更好的保護環境，來進行垃圾分類吧。
desc_en: Let's sort the waste in order to protect our environment.
desc_kr: 환경을 지키기 위해, 쓰레기를 분리수거해주세요.

desc: The wild Pokémons have often attacked the villagers in the town. Go and protect the villagers!
desc_tw: 野生的精靈最近暴亂，經常襲擊鎮上村民，請前去保護村民安全！
desc_en: The wild Pokémons have often attacked the villagers in the town. Go and protect the villagers!
desc_kr: 야생의 포켓몬들이 최근 폭동을 일으켜, 마을 주민을 습격하고 있습니다. 주민들을 지켜주세요!

name: Follow the target
desc: The police asked the trainer to assist in tracking the targets and reporting their whereabouts.
desc_tw: 員警請求訓練家説明跟蹤目標人物，並回饋行蹤。
desc_en: The police asked the trainer to assist in tracking the targets and reporting their whereabouts.
desc_kr: 경찰이 트레이너에게 타깃 인물을 추적하고 행적을 알려달라 요청했습니다.

name: Escort the Professor
desc: The professor has requested the Trainers Association to protect him and ensure his safe arrival at the destination.
desc_tw: 博士委託訓練家協會來護送自己，要求安全抵達目的地。
desc_en: The professor has requested the Trainers Association to protect him and ensure his safe arrival at the destination.
desc_kr: 박사님이 트레이너 협회에 자신을 목적지까지 안전하게 호송해달라 요청했습니다.

name: Escort the Document
desc: The mysterious organization requested for a trainer to protect and deliver the confidential documents.
desc_tw: 神秘機構委託訓練家來幫忙押運機密檔，完成後可獲得豐厚報酬。
desc_en: The mysterious organization requested for a trainer to protect and deliver the confidential documents.
desc_kr: 수수께끼의 기관이 트레이너에게 기밀문서 운송을 위탁했습니다. 완료하면 푸짐한 보수를 얻을 수 있습니다

name: Private Investigator
desc: The villagers privately requested help from the trainers to investigate the whereabouts of their missing partners.
desc_tw: 村民私下委託訓練家們來調查自己物件的行蹤。
desc_en: The villagers privately requested help from the trainers to investigate the whereabouts of their missing partners.
desc_kr: 마을 주민이 사적으로 트레이너들에게 대상의 행적을 조사해달라 위탁했습니다.

name: Alola Investigation
desc: Dispatch Pokémons to Alola region and find out whether there are wild Mews in the area.
desc_tw: 派遣精靈前往阿羅拉地區，調查當地是否有野生的夢幻出沒。
desc_en: Dispatch Pokémons to Alola region and find out whether there are wild Mews in the area.
desc_kr: 포켓몬을 알로라 지역으로 파견해, 야생의 뮤가 출몰했는지 조사하라 했습니다.

name: Soothe the Pokémon
desc: Soothe the Pokémons that hinders the citizens from traveling around in this city.
desc_tw: 把在本市擾亂市民正常出行的精靈安撫平定下來。
desc_en: Soothe the Pokémons that hinders the citizens from traveling around in this city.
desc_kr: 도시에서 시민들의 정상적인 외출을 방해하는 포켓몬을 달래주세요.

name: Kiwifruit
desc: Form a team of Pokémons to explore the forest and find kiwifruits.
desc_tw: 組織一隊精靈前往森林進行探索，需找一種名為奇異果實的食物。
desc_en: Form a team of Pokémons to explore the forest and find kiwifruits.
desc_kr: 포켓몬 팀을 꾸려 숲을 탐색하고, 키위라는 과일을 찾으세요.

name: Eliminate pests
desc: There's a pest infestation in the forest recently and there's a need for trainers to clear them with their Pokémons
desc_tw: 近期森林中的害蟲氾濫，需要各方精靈前去清除。
desc_en: There's a pest infestation in the forest recently and there's a need for trainers to clear them with their Pokémons
desc_kr: 최근에 숲에서 해충이 범람하여, 포켓몬을 보내 박멸이 필요함.

name: Pick berries
desc: It's the season of berries again! Organize an outing with the Pokémons to pick the berries!
desc_tw: 又到了樹果盛產的季節，和精靈組織一場採集樹果的郊遊吧！
desc_en: It's the season of berries again! Organize an outing with the Pokémons to pick the berries!
desc_kr: 과일 수확의 계절이 찾아왔습니다. 포켓몬들과 함께 과일을 따러 가세요!

name: Waste sorting
desc: Let's sort the waste in order to protect our environment.
desc_tw: 為了更好的保護環境，來進行垃圾分類吧。
desc_en: Let's sort the waste in order to protect our environment.
desc_kr: 환경을 지키기 위해, 쓰레기를 분리수거해주세요.

name: Missing Pokémon
desc: The trainer in town has lost his Pokémon. Help him find it.
desc_tw: 鎮上的訓練家把自己的精靈弄丟了，需要請求幫忙一起尋找。
desc_en: The trainer in town has lost his Pokémon. Help him find it.
desc_kr: 마을에서 어느 트레이너가 자신의 포켓몬을 잃어버렸답니다. 같이 찾아 주세요.

name: Spiritual Mentor
desc: Use Pokémons to comfort the lost villagers and relief the depressing mood.
desc_tw: 用精靈去溫暖失落的村民，釋放壓抑的心情。
desc_en: Use Pokémons to comfort the lost villagers and relief the depressing mood.
desc_kr: 낙심하는 마을 주민을 포켓몬으로 위로해 주고, 우울한 기분을 풀어주세요.

name: Help to find Pokémon
desc: Help rookie trainers train their Pokémons.
desc_tw: 幫助新手訓練家馴服自己的精靈。
desc_en: Help rookie trainers train their Pokémons.
desc_kr: 새로 온 트레이너의 포켓몬 훈련을 도와주세요.

name: Catch the criminal
desc: The police have found a Pokémon thief who has been wanted for years. Assist the police in their arrest!
desc_tw: 警方找到通緝多年偷盜精靈的小偷，協助員警進行抓捕！
desc_en: The police have found a Pokémon thief who has been wanted for years. Assist the police in their arrest!
desc_kr: 경찰이 수년간 수배한 포켓몬 도둑을 찾아냈습니다. 경찰을 도와 범인을 잡으세요!
